moment%20a%20new%20Russian%20submarine%20test-fired%20an%20intercontinental-range%20ballistic%20missile.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20final%20test%20before%20the%20strategic%20nuclear%20submarine%20can%20be%20deployed%2C%20Russia%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20sub%20can%20carry%2016%20of%20the%20Bulava%20missiles%2C%20and%20each%20missile%20can%20carry%20six%20nuclear%20warheads.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20new%20strategic%20nuclear%20submarine%20has%20successfully%20launched%20an%20intercontinental%20ballistic%20missile%2C%20it's%20defense%20ministry%20said%2C%20releasing%20video%20footage%20it%20said%20was%20from%20the%20test.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20test%20involved%20the%20firing%20of%20an%20intercontinental-range%20Bulava%20submarine-launched%20ballistic%20missile%20(SLBM)%20and%20was%20a%20significant%20step%20for%20the%20vessel.%20Decisions%20on%20the%20submarine's%20entry%20into%20service%20with%20the%20Russian%20navy%20will%20follow%20this%20test%2C%20the%20last%20of%20the%20state%20trials%2C%20Russia%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVideo%20footage%20from%20the%20defense%20ministry%20that%20was%20shared%20by%20Russian%20state%20media%20outlets%20on%20Sunday%20showed%20what%20they%20said%20was%20the%20newest%20Borei-class%20nuclear-powered%20ballistic%20missile%20submarine%20Imperator%20Alexander%20III%20launching%20an%20RSM-56%20Bulava%20ballistic%20missile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20missile%20flies%20up%20and%20soars%20across%20the%20sky%2C%20leaving%20a%20large%20trail%20of%20smoke%20behind%20it.%20Russia's%20defense%20ministry%20said%20that%20the%20test%20took%20place%20in%20the%20White%20Sea%20off%20Russia's%20northern%20coast%2C%20with%20the%20missile%20hitting%20a%20target%20on%20the%20Kura%20combat%20field%20on%20the%20far%20eastern%20Kamchatka%20peninsula.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20clas