nessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20about%20to%20be%20more%20up%20to%20date%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OpenAI%20chatbot%20will%20now%20have%20knowledge%20of%20the%20world%20up%20to%20April%202023%2C%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-dev-day-gets-ai-developers-hyped-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20first%20developer%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20ChatGPT%20was%20launched%20in%20November%202022%2C%20the%20chatbot%20could%20only%20answer%20questions%20based%20on%20information%20up%20to%20September%202021%20because%20of%20training%20limitations.%20That%20meant%20that%20the%20AI%20couldn't%20respond%20to%20prompts%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-crypto-ftx-alameda-scam-trial-verdict-prison-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20collapse%20of%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried's%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecrypto%20empire%20or%20the%202022%20US%20elections%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20just%20as%20annoyed%20as%20all%20of%20you%20%E2%80%94%20probably%20more%20%E2%80%94%20that%20GPT-4's%20knowledge%20about%20the%20world%20ended%20in%202021%2C%26quot%3B%20Altman%20said%20during%20his%20keynote.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20try%20to%20never%20let%20it%20get%20that%20out%20of%20date%20again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20update%20will%20only%20be%20available%20to%20paying%20users%20of%20GPT-4%20Turbo%20model%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-chatbots-like-chatgpt-work-explainer-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20latest%2C%20most%20advanced%20large%20language%20model%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20update%20is%20different%20from%20ChatGPT's%20web-browsing%20feature%20that%20was%20introduced%20in%20September.%20Th