2C%20Christopher%20Kise%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontrol%20your%20client.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20the%20first%20former%20US%20president%20to%20take%20the%20stand%20as%20a%20defendant%20in%20a%20court%20case%20in%20more%20than%20a%20century%2C%20complained%20in%20testimony%20about%20what%20he%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unfair%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20trial%26quot%3B%20brought%20by%20Democrats%20%26quot%3Bcoming%20after%20me%20from%2015%20different%20sides.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2077-year-old%20Trump%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20dark%20blue%20suit%20and%20tie%20with%20an%20American%20flag%20on%20his%20lapel%2C%20was%20sworn%20in%20shortly%20after%2010%3A00%20am%20(1500%20GMT)%20to%20begin%20his%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20his%20eldest%20sons%20Don%20Jr%20and%20Eric%2C%20and%20other%20Trump%20Organization%20executives%20are%20accused%20of%20exaggerating%20the%20value%20of%20their%20real%20estate%20assets%20by%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20obtain%20more%20favorable%20bank%20loans%20and%20insurance%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETestifying%20under%20oath%2C%20Trump%20dismissed%20allegations%20that%20the%20company's%20statements%20of%20financial%20condition%20were%20fraudulent%2C%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthey%20were%20not%20really%20documents%20that%20the%20banks%20paid%20much%20attention%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20value%20of%20the%20%26quot%3BTrump%20brand%26quot%3B%20was%20also%20not%20taken%20into%20account%20in%20the%20valuations%20of%20his%20real%20estate%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20became%20president%20because%20of%20my%20brand%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20under%20questioning%20from%20Kevin%20Wallace%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20New%20York%20attorney%20general's%20office%20which%20brought%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20taking%20the%20stand%2C%20Trump%2C%20the%20frontrunner%20for%20the%202024%20Republican%20presidential%20nomination%2C%20spoke%20to%20reporters%20outside%20the%20courtroom%2C%20denouncing%20the%20case%20as%20%26quot%3Belection%20interference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20sad%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20usually%20takes%20place%20in%20third%20world%20countries%20and%20banana%20republics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Numbers%2C%20my%20friends%2C%20don't%20lie'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20state%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20told%20reporters%20before%20Trump's%20arrival%20that%20the%20former%20president%20had%20%26quot%3Bconsistently%20misrepresented%20and%20inflated%20the%20value%20of%20his%20assets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20he%20takes%20the%20stand%2C%20I%20am%20certain%20that%20he%20will%20engage%20in%20name-calling%20and%20taunts%20and%20race-baiting%20and%20call%20this%20a%20witch%20hunt%2C%26quot%3B%20James%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20matters%20are%20the%20facts%20and%20the%20numbers.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20numbers%2C%20my%20friends%2C%20don't%20lie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20attacked%20James%2C%20who%20is%20Black%2C%20as%20%26quot%3Bracist%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20also%20gone%20after%20Engoron%2C%20calling%20the%20judge%20%26quot%3Bunhinged%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%26quot%3BTrump-hating%20radical%20left%2C%20Democrat%20operative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEngoron%20has%20responded%20by%20slapping%20Trump%20with%20%2415%2C000%20in%20fines%20for%20violating%20a%20partial%20gag%20order%20imposed%20after%20he%20bashed%20the%20judge's%20clerk%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump's%20testimony%20follows%20that%20of%20his%20sons%20Don%20Jr.%20and%20Eric%2C%20who%20took%20the%20stand%20last%20week%20and%20blamed%20accountants%20for%20any%20inaccuracies%20in%20the%20financial%20statements%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post%2C%20the%20last%20former%20president%20to%20testify%20publicly%20as%20a%20defendant%20was%20Theodore%20Roosevelt%2C%20who%20took%20the%20stand%20during%20a%201915%20libel%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20already%20given%20testimony%20twice%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20case%2C%20both%20times%20in%20closed-door%20depositions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFirst%20of%20several%20trials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETrump%20and%20his%20sons%20do%20not%20risk%20going%20to%20jail%2C%20but%20face%20up%20to%20%24250%20million%20in%20penalties%20and%20potential%20removal%20from%20the%20management%20of%20the%20family%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20opening%20arguments%2C%20Engoron%20ruled%20that%20James's%20office%20had%20already%20shown%20%26quot%3Bconclusive%20evidence%26quot%3B%20that%20Trump%20had%20overstated%20his%20net%20worth%20on%20financial%20documents%20by%20between%20%24812%20million%20and%20%242.2%20billion%20between%202014%20and%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20the%20judge%20ordered%20the%20liquidation%20of%20the%20companies%20managing%20the%20assets%20in%20question%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Trump%20Tower%20and%2040%20Wall%20Street%20skyscrapers%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20order%20is%20on%20hold%20pending%20appeal%2C%20but%20its%20potentially%20sweeping%20consequences%20highlight%20the%20high%20stakes%20for%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tycoon's%20daughter%2C%20Ivanka%20Trump%2C%20who%20left%20the%20Trump%20Organization%20in%202017%20to%20become%20a%20White%20House%20advisor%2C%20is%20not%20a%20codefendant%20in%20the%20case%20but%20has%20also%20been%20ordered%20to%20testify%2C%20possibly%20as%20soon%20as%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20civil%20fraud%20trial%20is%20one%20of%20several%20legal%20battles%20Trump%20faces%20as%20he%20seeks%20to%20recapture%20the%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20Trump%20--%20who%20was%20impeached%20twice%20while%20in%20office%20--%20faces%20a%20trial%20on%20charges%20that%20he%20conspired%20to%20overturn%20the%20results%20of%20the%202020%20election%2C%20which%20he%20lost%20to%20President%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699297380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fj6hvdaoo_trump_625x300_07_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-became-president-because-what-donald-trump-said-in-new-york-civil-fraud-trial-4551913%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20combative%20Donald%20Trump%20clashed%20repeatedly%20with%20the%20judge%20on%20Monday%20as%20he%20took%20the%20stand%20in%20the%20New%20York%20civil%20fraud%20case%20threatening%20to%20cripple%20his%20real%20estate%20empire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-became-president-because-what-donald-trump-said-in-new-york-civil-fraud-trial-4551913%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-became-president-because-what-donald-trump-said-in-new-york-civil-fraud-trial-4551913%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-became-president-because-what-donald-trump-said-in-new-york-civil-fraud-trial-4551913%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98American%20Valor%3A%20A%20Salute%20to%20Our%20Heroes%E2%80%99%20Veterans%20Day%20Special%20to%20Return%20Featuring%20Bradley%20Cooper%2C%20Tom%20Cruise%20and%20Michael%20Douglas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699297005000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F231104_AmValor_MainEvent-295.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1235781545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22