oken%20about%20a%20lot%20is%20'timed%20out'.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Angelo%20Mathews%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1260-angelo-mathews-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAngelo%20Mathews%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F792-shakib-al-hasan-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShakib%20Al%20Hasan%3C%2Fa%3E%20got%20a%20permanent%20place%20in%20the%20cricket%20history%20as%20the%20duo%20was%20involved%20in%20one%20of%20the%20rarest%20dismissals%20in%20cricket%2C%20that%20too%20in%20a%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20match.%20Former%20Sri%20Lanka%20captain%20Angelo%20Mathews%20was%20given%20'timed%20out'%20-%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20international%20cricket%20-%C2%A0%20with%20rival%20captain%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20appealing%20for%20it.%20The%20decision%20left%20the%20cricket%20world%20divided.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShakib%20was%20within%20the%20rules%20to%20appeal%20for%20the%20timed%20out%20decision.%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20played%20a%20big%20part%2C%20scoring%2082%2C%20as%20Sri%20Lanka%20failed%20to%20defend%20a%20279-run%20target%20against%20Bangladesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20our%20fielders%20came%20to%20me%20and%20said%20that%20if%20I%20appealed%2C%20he%20would%20be%20out.%20The%20umpire%20asked%20me%20if%20I%20was%20serious.%20It's%20in%20the%20laws%3B%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20it's%20right%20or%20wrong.%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20at%20war.%20Whatever%20I%20had%20to%20do%2C%20I%20did%20it.%20There%20will%20be%20debates.%20Today%20that%20(the%20time%20out)%20helped%2C%20I%20won't%20deny%20that!%26quot%3B%20Shakib%20Al%20Hasan%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20won%20the%20toss%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20hesitation%20in%20bowling%20first%20because%20we%20had%20trained%20here%20%5Bin%20the%20dew%5D.%20We%20had%20to%20bat%20deep.%20Luckily%20we%20got%20a%20big%20partnership.%20Shanto%20and%20I%20applied%20ourselves%20really%20well.%20We%20would%20have%20loved%20to%20finish%20early%20-%20with%20lesser%20wickets%20%5Blost%5D%20-%20but%20a%20win%20is%20a%20win.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Charith%20Asalanka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F110487-charith-asalanka-playerprofile%5C%22%3ECharith%20Asalanka%3C%2Fa%3E's%20century%20went%20in%20vain%20as%20Bangladesh%20defeated%20Sri%20Lanka%20by%20three%20wickets%20in%20an%20inconsequential%20match%20of%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20Delhi%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESent%20in%20to%20bat%2C%20middle-order%20batter%20Asalanka%20scored%20a%20105-ball%20108%2C%20while%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pathum%20Nissanka%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112358-pathum-nissanka-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPathum%20Nissanka%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Sadeera%20Samarawickrama%20made%20identical%20scores%20of%2041%20runs%20each%20to%20help%20Sri%20Lanka%20post%20279%20all%20out%20in%2049.3%20overs%20in%20a%20contest%20between%20teams%20which%20are%20out%20of%20semifinal%20contention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20scored%20the%20required%20runs%20in%2041.1%20overs%20for%20the%20loss%20of%20seven%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Sri%20Lankan%20innings%20was%20marred%20by%20an%20incident%20where%20Angelo%20Mathews%20became%20the%20first%20international%20cricketer%20to%20be%20'timed%20out'%20after%20not%20being%20ready%20to%20face%20the%20ball%20within%20two%20minutes%20of%20the%20fall%20of%20a%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2036-year-old%20walked%20out%20to%20bat%20after%20the%20dismissal%20of%20Samarawickrama%20but%20had%20some%20issues%20with%20his%20helmet%20strap%20and%20signalled%20for%20a%20replacement%2C%20prompting%20Bangladesh%20to%20appeal%20for%20a%20'time%20out'.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMathews%20was%20seen%20having%20a%20animated%20discussion%20with%20the%20umpires%20but%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20was%