y.com%2Fstory%2Fscientists-discover-oldest-ever-black-hole-and-say-it-could-explain-universes-mysteries-13002144%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Astronomers%20say%20they%20have%20discovered%20the%20oldest%20black%20hole%20yet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fscientists-discover-oldest-ever-black-hole-and-say-it-could-explain-universes-mysteries-13002144%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fscientists-discover-oldest-ever-black-hole-and-say-it-could-explain-universes-mysteries-13002144%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fscientists-discover-oldest-ever-black-hole-and-say-it-could-explain-universes-mysteries-13002144%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20Employee%20Loses%20Rs%201.6%20Crore%20Stock%20After%20Refusing%20To%20Return%20To%20Office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20software-development%20manager%20who%20was%20with%20the%20tech%20giant%20for%20over%20three%20years%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20after%20the%20company%20asked%20him%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office%20in%20the%20US.%20The%20employee%20had%20to%20forego%20company%20stocks%20worth%20%24200%2C000%20(about%20Rs%201.6%20crore).%20The%20man%20who%20has%20opted%20to%20stay%20anonymous%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.in%2Ftech%2Fnews%2Famazon-wanted-me-to-move-across-the-country-to-return-to-office-i-left-200000-in-unvested-stock-options-on-the-table-when-i-quit-%2Farticleshow%2F104928248.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EInsider%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20they%20were%20informed%20in%20May%20that%20they%20would%20need%20to%20report%20from%20the%20office%20in%20Seattle%20in%20June.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20employee%20said%20that%20they%20were%20%26quot%3Bblindsided%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20decision%20and%20felt%20that%20it%20was%20a%20betrayal%20of%20the%20company's%20original%20promise%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20work%20remotely.%20%26quot%3BI%20tried%20negotiating.%20I%20showed%20them%20an%20estimate%20I'd%20received%20to%20pack%20up%20my%20family%20and%20move%20us%20across%20the%20country%20with%20our%20livestock%20-%20it%20would%20have%20cost%20%24150%2C000%20-%20and%20asked%20what%20the%20relocation%20package%20would%20look%20like.%20I%20didn't%20get%20an%20answer%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20mounting%20pressure%20from%20the%20company%2C%20discussions%20arose%20about%20employees%20being%20less%20productive%20while%20working%20from%20home%2C%20despite%20lacking%20any%20data%20to%20substantiate%20these%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20then%20we%20were%20being%20told%2C%20'We%20don't%20have%20the%20data%2C%20we%20just%20know%20it's%20true'%20--%20a%20phrase%20so%20patently%20un-Amazonian%20that%20it%20became%20hard%20to%20sit%20there%20and%20preach%20leadership%20principles...%20It%20didn't%20make%20any%20sense.%20It%20still%20doesn't%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20ultimately%20quit%20his%20job%2C%20losing%20%24203%2C000%20in%20unvested%20stock.%20The%20former%20Amazon%20staff%20member%20is%20now%20employed%20at%20a%20company%20with%20another%20former%20Amazon%20colleague.%20He%20mentioned%20that%20his%20present%20role%20offers%20a%20similar%20salary%20to%20his%20previous%20one%2C%20yet%20it's%20clear%20they%20cannot%20rival%20Amazon's%20stock%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmazon%20spokesperson%20Brad%20Glasser%20told%20Insider%20via%20email%20that%20they%20couldn't%20confirm%20the%20employee's%20story.%20He%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20single%20anecdote%20could%20not%20characterise%20a%20company%20of%20Amazon's%20size.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Glasser%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BWe've%20repeatedly%20made%20our%20position%20clear%3A%20In%20February%2C%20we%20shared%20with%20employees%20that%20we'd%20be%20asking%20them%20to%20start%20coming%20into%20the%20office%20three%20or%20more%20days%20per%20week%20beginning%20in%20May%20because%20we%20believe%20it%20would%20yield%20the%20best%20long-term%20results%20for%20our%20customers%2C%20business%2C%20and%20culture.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20process%2C%20we've%20asked%20a%20relatively%20small%20percentage%20of%20our%20team%20to%20relocate%20to%20be%20in%20the%20same%20location%20as%20their%20teams.%20This%20isn't%20a%20one-size-fits-all%20approach%2C%20so%20team%20hubs%20and%20relocation%20timelines%20will%20vary%20based%20on%20a%20number%20of%20factors%2C%20and%20we're%20communicating%20with%20employees%20individually%20and%20providing%20relocation%20support.%20As%20is%20the%20case%20with%20any%20of%20our%20policies%2C%20we%20expect%20our%20team%20to%20follow%20them%20and%20will%20take%20appropriate%20action%20if%20someone%20chooses%20not%20to%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699289460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-04%2Fge98cqb_amazon-generic-_625x300_06_April_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-employee-loses-rs-1-6-crore-stock-after-refusing-to-return-to-office-4551744%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20former%20Amazon%20employee%20revealed%20that%20he%20ultimately%20quit%20his%20job%2C%20losing%20%24203%2C000%20in%20unvested%20stock.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-employee-loses-rs-1-6-crore-stock-after-refusing-to-return-to-office-4551744%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-employee-loses-rs-1-6-crore-stock-after-refusing-to-return-to-office-4551744%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famazon-employee-loses-rs-1-6-crore-stock-after-refusing-to-return-to-office-4551744%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Renew%20Power%20pla