kquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Iranian%20President%20shared%20with%20Modi%20his%20assessment%20of%20the%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia.%20Both%20leaders%20also%20emphasised%20on%20the%20need%20to%20prevent%20escalation%2C%20ensure%20continued%20humanitarian%20aid%2C%20and%20early%20restoration%20of%20peace%20and%20stability.%20They%20also%20reviewed%20progress%20in%20India-Iran%20bilateral%20cooperation%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cwelcomed%20focus%20and%20priority%20accorded%20to%20Chabahar%20port%20in%20Iran%20for%20improving%20regional%20connectivity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20agreed%20to%20remain%20in%20touch%20given%20their%20shared%20interest%20in%20regional%20peace%2C%20security%2C%20and%20stability%2C%20the%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20Modi%20has%20spoken%20with%20the%20leaders%20of%20Israel%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Egypt%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE)%20to%20discuss%20the%20ongoing%20situation%20in%20West%20Asia.%C2%A0Modi%20had%20first%20spoken%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20to%20reiterate%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-reiterates-solidarity-phone-call-netanyahu-israel-hamas%5C%22%3Esolidarity%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20with%20the%20Israelis%20on%20October%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EModi%20engaged%20in%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fmodi-palestine-authority-president-mahmoud-abbas-call-israel-gaza%5C%22%3Econversation%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20Palestinian%20Authority%20President%20Mahmoud%20Abbas%20on%20October%2019%2C%20two%20days%20after%20the%20explosion%20at%20Gaza%20City%E2%80%99s%20al-Ahli%20Hospital%20had%20incited%20outrage%20in%20the%20Arab%20world.%20During%20their%20discussion%2C%20Modi%20subtly%20adjusted%20India%E2%80%99s%20position%20by%20reaffirming%20its%20longstanding%20support%20for%20the%20two-state%20solution.%C2%A0The%20third%20regional%20leader%20that%20Modi