nd%20my%20father%20was%20safe%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds%20with%20a%20sigh%20of%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%202022%20study%20estimates%20that%20India%20reports%20at%20least%2064%2C000%20snakebite%20deaths%20every%20year%2C%20especially%20making%20people%20living%20in%20the%20rural%20hinterlands%20more%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-2-1699278240-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333674%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20doctor%20couple%2C%20Sadanand%20and%20Pallavi%20Raut%2C%20has%20saved%20the%20lives%20of%20at%20least%206%2C000%20snakebite%20victims%20in%20the%20region%20as%20part%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Zero%20Snakebite%20Death%E2%80%99%20in%20Narayangaon.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKiran%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThat%20day%2C%20the%20couple%20saved%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20life.%20Like%20us%2C%20people%20in%20the%20stretch%20of%20about%20150%20km%20rely%20on%20his%20treatment.%20He%20is%20a%20saviour%20for%20such%20patients.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMission%20Zero%20Snake%20Bite%20Deaths%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Umbraj%20village%20in%20Pune%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20Raut%20graduated%20in%20general%20medicine%20in%201992.%20The%20physician%20started%20practising%20in%20the%20nearby%20village%20of%20Narayangaon%2C%20a%20tribal%20dominated%20hilly%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20motive%20to%20serve%20the%20community%20in%20the%20town%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20their%20own%20practice%20in%20the%20same%20year.%20But%20they%20got%20their%20life%E2%80%99s%20purpose%20when%20a%20young%20girl%20was%20brought%20to%20their%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20a%20worker%20on%20my%20friend%E2%80%99s%20farm%20called%20and%20informed%20me%20that%20his%20daughter%20was%20bitten%20by%20a%20cobra.%20She%20had%20severe%20pain%20at%20the%20site%20and%20had%20difficulty%20in%20breathing.%20I%20told%20him%20to%20immediately%20bring%20the%20child%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Unfortunately%2C%20she%20died%20on%20the%20way.%20She%20was%20just%20eight%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20doctor%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDisturbed%20by%20the%20incident%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20decided%20that%20from%20thereon%2C%20he%20would%20not%20let%20any%20person%20in%20the%20village%20die%20of%20snakebite.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-3-1-1699278286.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%20India%2C%20around%2090%20percent%20of%20snakebites%20are%20caused%20by%20the%20%E2%80%98big%20four%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20Common%20krait%2C%20Indian%20cobra%2C%20Russell's%20viper%2C%20and%20the%20Saw%20Scaled%20Viper.%5C%22%20