on%20krait%2C%20Indian%20cobra%2C%20Russell%E2%80%99s%20viper%2C%20and%20the%20Saw%20Scaled%20Viper.%20If%20there%20is%20a%20delay%20in%20administering%20the%20anti-snake%20venom%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20says%2C%20chances%20are%20the%20snake%20bite%20will%20cause%20grave%20organ%20damage%2C%20or%20prove%20to%20be%20fatal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20realised%20that%20usually%20critically%20ill%20patients%20had%20to%20go%20to%20cities%20for%20treatment%20as%20there%20was%20no%20ambulance%20or%20support%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20many%20would%20die%20on%20their%20way%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Those%20who%20could%20not%20go%20to%20the%20city%20would%20visit%20faith%20healers%20and%20waste%20the%20golden%20hour%20for%20the%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20found%20that%20medical%20officers%20at%20the%20primary%20health%20centres%20would%20be%20reluctant%20to%20treat%20such%20cases%20as%20they%20either%20lacked%20antivenoms%20or%20necessary%20equipment%20such%20as%20ventilator%20support.%20They%20lack%20training%20to%20handle%20such%20emergency%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20started%20equipping%20his%20hospital%20with%20life%20saving%20equipment%20like%20cardiac%20monitors%2C%20ventilators%2C%20and%20oxygen%20cylinders%2C%20so%20that%20he%20could%20save%20lives%20at%20the%20local%20level.%20Over%20the%20past%2028%20years%2C%20his%20efforts%20have%20turned%20into%20a%20mission%20that%20aims%20at%20achieving%20zero%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F78205%2Findiansnakes-jose-louies-snakebites-app%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esnakebite%20deaths%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20Dos%20%26amp%3B%20Don%E2%80%99ts%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20get%20at%20least%20200%20snakebite%20cases%20every%20year.%20Monsoons%20are%20hectic%20when%20at%20least%2012%20patients%20are%20rushed%20to%20the%20medical%20facility%20in%20a%20day.%20Without%20any%20trained%20medical%20staff%20support%2C%20the%20couple%20works%20round%20the%20clock.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20also%20conducts%20awareness%20programs%20in%20villages%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20forest%20departments%2C%20and%20medical%20colleges.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1699278306-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333676%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20conducts%20awareness%20programs%20in%20villages%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20forest%20departments%2C%20and%20medical%20colleges.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F188596%2Fmumbai-woman-snake-bite-what-to-do-dharavi-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20cases%20of%20snakebites%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20suspected%2C%20patients%20should%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20hospital%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%20Before%20coming%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20family%20should%20check%20the%20availability%20of%20the%20doctor%20and%20antivenom%20at%20the%20facility.%20They%20should%20not%20waste%20time%20visiting%20faith%20healers%20or%20quacks.%20They%20should%20also%20not%20cut%20or%20tie%20the%20site%20of%20snakebite.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20a%20snake%20bite%2C%20the%20person%20starts%20panicking.%20It%20can%20increase%20the%20risk%20of%20high%20blood%20pressure.%20The%20family%20should%20assure%20the%20person%20that%20they%20do%20not%20need%20to%20worry%20as%20timely%20treatment%20will%20save%20their%20lives.%20Also%2C%20a%20person%20should%20not%20walk%20or%20run%20as%20blood%20will%20circulate%20to%20the%20heart%20and%20brain.%20The%20patient%20should%20be%20transferred%20safely%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20a%20lateral%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Sadanand%20informs%20that%20with%20intensive%20care%20management%20and%20administering%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F158165%2Fiit-delhi-kerala-floods-snakes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eantivenom%20doses%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20lives%20can%20be%20saved.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20been%20providing%20free%20treatment%20at%20sub-divisional%20government%20hospital%20Manchar%20for%20the%20last%2025%20years%20and%20regularly%20training%20medical%20officers%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20this%20mission%2C%20the%20couple%20also%20conducts%20awareness%20programs%20in%20villages%2C%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20forest%20departments%2C%20and%20medical%20colleges.%20Recently%2C%20they%20organised%20awareness%20programmes%20in%20Kolhapur%2C%20Satara%2C%20and%20Pune%20districts%20and%20claim%20to%20have%20trained%2010%2C000%20students%20and%202%2C000%20teachers%20in%20tribal%20schools%20to%20help%20them%20identify%20venomous%20and%20nonvenomous%20snakes%2C%20and%20the%20dos%20and%20don%E2%80%99ts%20in%20snakebite%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1-1699278319.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Sadanand%20was%20awarded%20the%20Arogya%20Ratna%20Award%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra%20last%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1-1699278319.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1-1699278319-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1-1699278319-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1-1699278319-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Fsnakebite-1-1699278319-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333677%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Sadanand%20was%20awarded%20the%20Arogya%20Ratna%20Award%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra%20last%20year.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20says%20that%20they%20trained%201%2C500%20ASHA%20(Accredited%20Social%20Health%20Activist)%20workers%20in%20the%20Pune%20district%20in%20handling%20snakebite%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20his%20work%2C%20Dr%20Sadanand%20was%20awarded%20the%20Arogya%20Ratna%20Award%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Maharashtra%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20his%20work%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20we%20started%20the%20mission%2C%20there%20had%20been%20no%20mortality%20at%20the%20hospital%20level.%20Also%2C%20we%20gained%20the%20trust%20of%20the