0over%20the%20past%20couple%20of%20months.%20The%20man%20from%20Beed%20was%20on%20a%20fast%20unto%20death%20with%20one%20demand%3A%20provide%2016%25%20reservation%20to%20the%20Maratha%20community%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%202%2C%20Jarange-Patil%20ended%20his%20nine-day%20fast%20after%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20promised%20to%20resolve%20the%20reservation%20issue%20in%20two%20months.%20But%20even%20after%20ending%20the%20fast%2C%20Jarange-Patil%20remains%20in%20the%20driver%E2%80%99s%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20renewed%20demand%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20for%20the%20Maratha%20reservation%20is%20not%20new.%20The%20demand%20has%20been%20around%20since%201997%20and%20the%20protests%20were%20at%20their%20peak%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202018%2C%20then%20chief%20minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20enacted%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Reservation%20for%20Socially%20and%20Educationally%20Backward%20Classes%20(SEBC)%20Act.%20This%20legislation%20granted%20a%2016%25%20reservation%20in%20education%20and%20government%20jobs%20specifically%20for%20the%20Maratha%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Bombay%20high%20court%20in%202019%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcaste%2Fbombay-hc-upholds-validity-of-maratha-quota-but-wants-it-reduced-to-12-13%5C%22%3Eupheld%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20quota%2C%20but%20wanted%20it%20reduced%20to%2012-13%25.%20In%202021%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmaratha-quota-case-sc-declares-reservation-over-50-as-unconstitutional%5C%22%3Escrapped%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%2C%20citing%20the%2050%25%20cap%20on%20total%20reservations%20established%20in%201992.%20The%20court%20maintained%20that%20there%20were%20no%20%E2%80%9Cexceptional%20circumstances%E2%80%9D%20or%20an%20%E2%80%9Cextraordinary%20situation%E2%80%9D%20in%20Maharashtra%20that%20warranted%20the%20state%20government%20exceeding%20this%20limit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20gained%20momentum%20once%20again%20in%20September.%20A%20protest%20in%20Jalna%20turned%20violent%20and%20videos%20of%20the%20police%20lathi-charging%20Maratha%20protestors%20spread%20like%20wildfire.%20Suddenly%2C%20Jarange-Patil%20became%20a%20household%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20commissions%20have%20said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Mandal%20Commission%20report%20did%20not%20consider%20Marathas%20in%20Maharashtra%20to%20be%20a%20backward%20community%20and%20thus%2C%20did%20not%20recommend%20that%20it%20should%20classified%20as%20part%20of%20reservations%20for%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs).%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202008%2C%20a%20committee%20commissioned%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20and%20led%20by%20retired%20judge%20R.M.%20Bapat%20released%20a%20report%20rejecting%20the%20idea%20of%20reservations%20for%20Marathas.%20Six%20years%20later%2C%20in%202014%2C%20another%20committee%20chaired%20by%20Narayan%20Rane%20%5Ba%20Congress%20minister%20then%2C%20a%20BJP%20minister%20now%5D%20presented%20a%20contrasting%20report.%20This%20committee%20argued%20that%20Marathas%20constituted%2032%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population%20and%20required%20economic%20support%2C%20thereby%20justifying%20the%20need%20for%20reservations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20chief%20minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%E2%80%99s%20government%20approved%20a%20proposal%20to%20reserve%2016%25%20of%20government%20jobs%20and%20seats%20in%20educational%20institutions%20for%20Marathas%2C%20along%20with%205%25%20for%20Muslims.%20An%20ordinance%20was%20swiftly%20passed%20to%20enforce%20this%20decision.%20However%2C%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20ordinance%20was%20promptly%20contested%20in%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20stay%20order%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20complications%20within%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Marathas%20are%20not%20a%20homogenous%20unit.%20There%20are%20various%20sub-castes%20within%20the%20Marathas%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Kunbis.%20The%20Kunbi%20community%20has%20a%20primarily%20agrarian%20background.%20They%20have%20traditionally%20been%20involved%20in%20farming%20and%20agriculture.%20Marathas%20are%20a%20landed%20caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201960s%2C%20Panjabrao%20Deshmukh%2C%20a%20prominent%20figure%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20conducted%20a%20survey%20challenging%20the%20Maratha%20identity%20of%20the%20farming%20community.%20He%20proposed%20that%20they%20were%20not%20Marathas%20but%20rather%20%E2%80%98Kunbis%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20distinction%20that%20was%20controversial%20at%20the%20time%20and%20received%20widespread%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20era%2C%20farmers%20in%20the%20Vidarbha%20region%20of%20Maharashtra%20obtained%20certificates%20identifying%20themselves%20as%20Kunbis%20in%20substantial%20numbers.%20However%2C%20farmers%20in%20the%20Marathwada%20and%20western%20Maharashtra%20region%20questioned%20whether%20they%20should%20be%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%98Other%20Backward%20Classes%E2%80%99%20(OBCs)%2C%20raising%20doubts%20about%20their%20traditional%20status%20as%20landowners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20four%20decades%2C%20the%20Maratha%20farmers%20from%20the%20former%20ashram%20schools%20in%20Vidarbha%20now%20benefit%20from%20reservations%20under%20the%20Kunbi%20category.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Maratha%20farmers%20in%20Marathwada%20find%20themselves%20excluded%20from%20the%20Maratha%20reservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20agitation%20by%20Jarange-Patil%20demands%20a%20blanket%20reservation%20for%20all%20Marathas%20under%20the%20Kunbi%20caste%20certificate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBJP%20and%20Maratha%20agitation%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20demand%20has%20larger%20implications%20for%20OBC%20communities%20and%20also%20for%20the%20BJP.%20The%20former%20are%20anxious%20that%20if%20the%20Marathas%20are%20included%20in%20the%20quota%2C%20it%20may%20dilute%20their%20share.%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20the%20state%20faces%20challenges%20in%20maintaining%20unity%20among%20its%20coalition%20allies%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20the%20rebel%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20%E2%80%93%20while%20also%20appeasing%20its%20core%20OBC%20voter%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20discontent%20within%20the%20OBC%20community%2C%20the%20BJP%20launched%20the%20%E2%80%98OBC%20Jagar%20Yatra%2C%E2%80%99%20starting%20in%20the%20Vidarbha%20region.%20This%20initiative%20aims%20to%20emphasise%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20commitment%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20OBC%20community%20and%20assure%20them%20that%20their%20reservation%20will%20not%20be%20compromised%20for%20the%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidarbha%2C%20a%20stronghold%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20before%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20rise%20in%202014%2C%20holds%20significant%20political%20influence%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20boasting%20ten%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%2062%20Assembly%20seats%20out%20of%20288.%20However%2C%20the%20BJP%20faces%20a%20growing%20challenge%20from%20a%20resurgent%20Congress%20in%20Vidarbha%2C%20where%20the%20party%20has%2015%20of%20its%2045%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20also%20saw%20some%20OBC%20leaders%20expressing%20discontent%20during%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%E2%80%99%20tenure%20as%20chief%20minister%20(2014-2019)%2C%20Some%2C%20like%20Pankaja%20Munde%20and%20Prakash%20Mehta%2C%20were%20apparently%20sidelined%2C%20while%20Eknath%20Khadse%20joined%20the%20NCP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20internal%20challenges%20threaten%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20stability%20in%20the%20region%2C%20adding%20complexity%20to%20the%20ongoing%20Maratha-OBC%20reservation%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBack%20to%20the%20present%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20MPs%2C%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmaratha-reservation-row-shiv-sena-mps-resign-over-maratha-quota-demand-hingoli-nashik-2455874-2023-10-31%5C%22%3Eloyalists%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20chief%20minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20have%20resigned%20to%20support%20the%20agitation%2C%20while%20the%20protests%20have%20turned%20violent%20and%20targeted%20lawmakers%20in%20parts%20of%20Maharashtra.%20The%20issue%20has%20the%20potential%20of%20ballooning%20into%20a%20full-blown%20political%20issue%20in%20Maharashtra%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20even%20though%20Jarange-Patil%20has%20ended%20his%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20will%20the%20Marathas%20get%20reservations%3F%20Will%20the%20OBCs%20accept%20it%3F%20Will%20the%20BJP%20avert%20a%20political%20crisis%20in%20Maharashtra%3F%20These%20are%20some%20important%20questions%20which%20have%20no%20answers%20at%20this%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699278339000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F06113902%2FUntitled-design-1-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanoj-jarange-patil-maratha-agitation-political-crisis-maharashtra%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20after%20ending%20his%20fast%2C%20Manoj%20Jarange-Patil%20remains%20in%20the%20driver%E2%80%99s%20seat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanoj-jarange-patil-maratha-agitation-political-crisis-maharashtra%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Chandameta%2C%20A%20Former%20Maoist%20Urges%20Villagers%20To%20Vote%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06190130%2FPandu-Markam.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChandameta%2C%20Chhattisgarh%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20surrendered%20Maoist%20in%20Chandameta%20village%20in%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20Bastar%20division%20is%20urging%20residents%20of%20his%20village%20to%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20on%20November%207.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPandu%20Markam%2C%2045%2C%20worked%20as%20a%20low-level%20ground%20worker%20and%20joined%20the%20Maoists%20at%20an%20early%20age.%20He%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Chetna%20Natya%20Mandali%2C%20the%20cultural%20wing%20of%20the%20banned%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Maoist)%20that%20uses%20dance%2C%20poetry%20and%20street%20plays%20as%20a%20means%20of%20political%20propaganda%20among%20villagers%20to%20build%20support%20for%20the%20Maoist%20cause.%20His%20other%20tasks%20included%20taking%20villagers%20to%20dig%20up%20the%20mountains%20that%20surround%20Chandameta%2C%20behind%20which%20lay%20Odisha%2C%20and%20providing%20Maoists%20with%20food%20and%20rations%20from%20his%20village.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarkam%2C%20who%20had%20a%20reward%20on%20his%20head%2C%20surrendered%20in%20October%20last%20year%20after%20Diwali.%20Under%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20government%E2%80%99s%20Naxal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcgpolice.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fsurrender-policy-2015.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurrender%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20rehabilitation%20policy%2C%20Markam%20received%20Rs%2010%2C000%20upon%20his%20surrender.%20While%20the%20rules%20also%20state%20that%20he%20is%20eligible%20to%20get%20the%20sum%20that%20was%20his%20reward%2C%20he%20is%20yet%20to%20receive%20it%20as%20his%20file%20is%20still%20pending.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20visits%20his%20family%20%E2%80%93%20a%20wife%20and%20eleven%20children%20%E2%80%93%20but%20he%20cannot%20live%20with%20them%20as%20his%20life%20continues%20to%20be%20under%20threat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20do%20feel%20scared%20for%20my%20life%20since%20I%20have%20come%20over%20to%20this%20side.%20But%20I%20was%20tired%20of%20working%20for%20them.%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20time%20on%20my%20farm%2C%20be%20with%20my%20family.%20When%20I%20would%20come%20home%20for%20a%20few%20days%2C%20my%20family%20would%20be%20upset%20that%20I%20had%20come%20for%20a%20short%20period.%20When%20they%20(Maoists)%20would%20call%20me%2C%20I%20would%20have%20to%20leave%20again%20and%20if%20I%20went%20even%20a%20few%20days%20late%2C%20they%20would%20verbally%20abuse%20me%20and%20question%20me%20about%20what%20I%20was%20doing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUntil%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20Chandameta%20was%20a%20Maoist%20stronghold.%20Almost%20every%20family%20in%20the%20village%20had%20a%20member%20who%20worked%20with%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaoists%20have%20receded%20in%20the%20village%20after%20a%20CRPF%20camp%20was%20set%20up%20less%20than%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06190236%2FA-smarak-set-up-by-Maoists-in-Chandameta-when-the-village-was-a-stronghold-untill-less-than-two-years-ago.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06190236%2FA-smarak-set-up-by-Maoists-in-Chandameta-when-the-village-was-a-stronghold-untill-less-than-two-years-ago.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06190236%2FA-smarak-set-up-by-Maoists-in-Chandameta-when-the-village-was-a-stronghold-untill-less-than-two-years-ago-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06190236%2FA-smarak-set-up-by-Maoists-in-Chandameta-when-the-village-was-a-stronghold-untill-less-than-two-years-ago-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683773%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20smarak%20set%20up%20by%20Maoists%20in%20Chandameta%20when%20the%20village%20was%20a%20stronghold%20until%20less%20than%20two%20years%20ago.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandameta%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Fchhattisgarh%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-residents-of-over-120-villages-in-maoist-hit-bastar-to-vote-in-their-own-villages-for-first-time-since-independence-2725287%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E120-odd%20villages%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20Maoist-influenced%20Bastar%20division%20where%20voters%20can%20exercise%20their%20franchise%20in%20their%20own%20place%20of%20residence%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBastar%20division%20includes%20seven%20districts%20and%20has%2012%20of%20the%2020%20assembly%20constituencies%20which%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20in%20the%20first%20of%20two%20phases%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20handler%20for%20the%20Maoists%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Markam%20would%20rally%20villagers%20against%20the%20government%2C%20telling%20them%20that%20only%20the%20%E2%80%9Cparty%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20able%20to%20help%20them%20while%20the%20government%20would%20not%20do%20anything%20for%20their%20development.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20trained%20in%20how%20to%20speak%20to%20villagers%20and%20to%20tell%20them%20not%20to%20fight%20among%20themselves%2C%20and%20to%20resolve%20issues%20through%20dialogue%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20also%20tasked%20with%20getting%20rations%20from%20the%20villagers%20and%20providing%20them%20to%20the%20Naxals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20villagers%20would%20get%20angry%20with%20me%20and%20curse%20at%20me%20for%20getting%20them%20to%20their%20houses%20for%20rations.%20They%20would%20tell%20me%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20rations%20to%20feed%20ourselves%20but%20you%20bring%20them%20here%20and%20we%20have%20to%20give%20them%20whatever%20little%20we%20have.%20But%20I%20had%20to%20bring%20them%20there%2C%20give%20them%20the%20rations%20%E2%80%93%20otherwise%20I%20would%20be%20cursed%20at%20as%20well%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20367px)%2085vw%2C%20367px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22367%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22303%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMarkam%20said%20that%20he%20joined%20the%20Maoists%20when%20he%20was%20young%20but%20could%20not%20remember%20the%20year%20or%20how%20old%20he%20was%20then.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20told%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98Where%20will%20you%20go%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20join%20us%3F%20You%20will%20have%20to%20live%20here.%E2%80%99%20I%20did%20not%20have%20an%20option%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20working%20for%20the%20Maoists%2C%20Markam%20in%20his%20testimony%20to%20security%20officials%20said%20that%20he%20had%20taken%20villagers%20from%20the%20area%20to%20dig%20up%20mountains%20in%20Jhiram%20Ghati%20for%20the%202013%20Sukma%20attack%20that%20killed%20Congress%20leader%20Mahendra%20Karma%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20entire%20top%20state%20leadership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20attack%2C%20Markam%20said%20that%20he%20was%20tasked%20to%20bring%20a%20group%20to%20the%20village%20to%20give%20them%20food.%20As%20a%20ground-level%20worker%2C%20he%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20ever%20meet%20the%20top%20leaders%20and%20did%20not%20know%20anyone%E2%80%99s%20names.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20came%20here%20to%20eat%20food.%20They%20were%20saying%20%E2%80%98we%20finished%20Mahendra%20Karma%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20the%20polling%20booth%2C%20his%20village%20has%20seen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-in-chandameta-with-electricity-roads-and-water-a-polling-booth-for-the-first-time%5C%22%3Emany%20developments%3C%2Fa%3E%20recently%3A%20electricity%20arrived%20only%20last%20week%2C%20a%20proper%20road%20was%20built%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20and%20mobile%20phone%20towers%20were%20installed%20recently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20the%2080%20families%20that%20live%20in%20the%20village%2C%20almost%20all%20have%20a%20member%20who%20has%20joined%20the%20Maoists%20at%20some%20point.%20While%20many%20have%20been%20released%2C%20about%2010%20members%20of%20the%20village%20are%20still%20lodged%20in%20Jagdalpur%20Central%20Jail%20for%20allegedly%20helping%20Maoists%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20the%20government%20has%20provided%20road%2C%20electricity%20here.%20I%20am%20telling%20people%20to%20go%20and%20vote.%20Earlier%2C%20I%20would%20tell%20the%20villagers%20not%20to%20vote%20because%20the%20government%20will%20not%20give%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Markam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699277874000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06190130%2FPandu-Markam.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3