a-ramsess-marvel_6350506.png%3F20231106140347%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftaraja-ramsess-marvel-stuntman-and-three-of-his-children-die-after-car-crash-13001929%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20stuntman%20best%20known%20for%20his%20work%20in%20Black%20Panther%20and%20Avengers%3A%20Endgame%20has%20died%20in%20a%20car%20crash%20that%20also%20killed%20three%20of%20his%20children%2C%20his%20mother%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A124%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ftaraja-ramsess-marvel-stuntman-and-three-of-his-children-die-after-car-crash-13001929%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftaraja-ramsess-marvel-stuntman-and-three-of-his-children-die-after-car-crash-13001929%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Ftaraja-ramsess-marvel-stuntman-and-three-of-his-children-die-after-car-crash-13001929%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20It%20Is%20Delhi's%20Annual%20Pollution%20Season%20-%20Who%20Can%20Stop%20This%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20is%20choking%20once%20again.%20Thick%2C%20toxic%20smog%20has%20engulfed%20the%20national%20capital%20and%20its%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20making%20Delhi%20the%20most%20polluted%20place%20in%20the%20world.%20The%20air%20quality%20crossed%20the%20'500'%20danger%20mark%20on%20November%203.%20The%20PM2.5%20concentration%20exceeded%20the%20safe%20limit%20of%2060%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre%20by%20seven%20to%20eight%20times%20at%20many%20spots.%20Schools%20have%20been%20shut%20(barring%20Class%2010%2C12)%20and%20the%20odd-even%20rule%20for%20cars%20will%20return%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGovernment%20agencies%20have%20warned%20that%20pollution%20levels%20could%20worsen%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20over%20the%20next%2015-20%20days%20due%20to%20a%20surge%20in%20farm%20fires%20in%20neighbouring%20Punjab%2C%20along%20with%20the%20expected%20drop%20in%20temperature%20and%20air%20speed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20brown%20haze%20has%20almost%20been%20a%20new%20season%20in%20Delhi%2C%20punctually%20arriving%20every%20October%20as%20the%20air%20becomes%20cooler.%20Winter%20in%20Delhi%20is%20morphing%20into%20pollution%20season%20that%20lasts%20till%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20four%20months%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bair-pocalypse%26quot%3B%20inspires%20headlines%2C%20discussions%20and%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20February%2C%20the%20subject%20of%20pollution%20is%20forgotten%20by%20people%2C%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments%2C%20and%20political%20parties.%20The%20courts%2C%20too%2C%20get%20a%20break%20from%20petitions%20on%20it.%20Done%20and%20dusted%2C%20until%20the%20next%20%26quot%3Bsepia%20season%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReasons%20For%20Yearly%20Smog%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20The%20average%20resident%20of%20Delhi%20loses%20up%20to%2012%20years%20of%20their%20life%20to%20air%20pollution%2C%20a%20study%20suggested%20recently.%20According%20to%20official%20figures%2C%20in%202022%2C%20Delhi's%20air%20was%20considered%20%26quot%3Bgood%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bsatisfactory%26quot%3B%20on%20only%2068%20days.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20sources%20of%20air%20pollution%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20is%20paddy%20stubble%20burning%20in%20the%20neighbouring%20states%20of%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Stubble%20(parali)%20burning%20accounts%20for%20about%2025%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%3B%20satellite%20images%20captured%20more%20than%201%2C000%20such%20fires%20burning%20in%20Punjab%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%20find%20this%20a%20cheap%20and%20effective%20way%20of%20clearing%20mowed%20fields%20after%20harvest%2C%20in%20preparation%20for%20the%20next%20rabi%20crop.%20The%20governments%20of%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20have%20failed%20to%20sensitise%20farmers%20or%20create%20awareness%20about%20green%20methods%20like%20the%20Pusa%20bio-decomposer%2C%20a%20technology%20developed%20by%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Agricultural%20Research%20(ICAR).%20This%20initiative%20was%20aimed%20at%20naturally%20decomposing%20paddy%20stubble%2C%20effectively%20converting%20it%20into%20valuable%20manure.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVehicles%20are%20also%20a%20major%20component%20of%20the%20toxic%20fume%2C%20along%20with%20dust%20from%20construction%20sites.%20The%20Delhi%20government%20hardly%20enforces%20dust%20control%20regulations.%20Landfill%20fires%20throughout%20the%20year%20exacerbate%20the%20crisis%2C%20because%20the%20build-up%20of%20methane%20generates%20toxic%20fumes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20health%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20The%20average%20concentration%20of%20particularly%20harmful%20PM2.5%20particles%20-%20which%20can%20enter%20the%20bloodstream%20and%20cause%20heart%20disease%20and%20respiratory%20problems%20-%20is%2098%20micrograms%20per%20cubic%20metre.%20That%20is%20nearly%2020%20times%20the%20level%20considered%20safe%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation.%20Coughing%2C%20breathing%20problems%2C%20watery%20eyes%20have%20become%20a%20common%20problem%20among%20people%20because%20of%20smog.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAir%20pollution%20is%20a%20serious%20problem%20for%20all%20age%20groups%20and%20affects%20everybody.%20It%20affects%20even%20pregnant%20women%2C%20which%20lead%20to%20various%20birth%20defects%2C%20premature%20deliveries%20etc.%20Children%20are%20commonly%20affected%20by%20asthma%2C%20pneumonia%2C%20and%20breathing%20difficulties%2C%20which%20may%20require%20ventilator%20support%20sometimes.%20It%20may%20later%20lead%20to%20chronic%20obstructive%20pulmonary%20disease%20and%20lung%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Vikas%20Chaudhary%2C%20paediatric%20consultant%20at%20Fortis%20Hospital%2C%20Shalimar%20Bagh%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitics%20over%20pollution%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20ruling%20Delhi%20for%20the%20past%20nine%20years%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20bold%20steps%20to%20check%20pollution.%20Installing%20two%20expensive%20but%20ineffective%20smog%20towers%3B%20the%20odd-even%20rule%20for%20cars%3B%20and%20sprinkling%20water%20on%20roads%20are%20symbolic%20gestures%20to%20hoodwink%20citizens.%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20are%20both%20ruled%20by%20AAP%2C%20but%20that%20has%20not%20helped%20reduce%20or%20control%20farm%20fires%20in%20Punjab.%20AAP%20leaders%20in%20Delhi%20are%20quick%20to%20point%20at%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20but%20their%20pollution%20mitigation%20plan%20has%20been%20in%20vain.%20Taking%20any%20action%20against%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%20by%20way%20of%20a%20ban%20on%20stubble%20burning%20or%20penalty%20would%20negatively%20impact%20AAP's%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20it%20certainly%20will%20not%20risk.%20This%20comes%20at%20a%20huge%20cost%20to%20millions%20of%20lives%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20opposition%20BJP%20in%20Delhi%20has%20hardly%20helped%2C%20other%20than%20add%20to%20the%20political%20noise.%20The%20Centre%20has%20offered%20no%20solution%20to%20this%20yearly%20menace.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Courts%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20recently%20pulled%20up%20the%20forest%20department%20for%20recklessly%20allowing%20the%20cutting%20of%20trees%20without%20any%20reason%2C%20and%20held%20it%20responsible%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20mess%20that%20the%20Capital%20is%20in%20because%20of%20pollution%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2031%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20directed%20Delhi%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Rajasthan%20to%20file%20affidavits%20listing%20their%20steps%20to%20control%20air%20pollution%20after%20noting%20that%20efforts%20so%20far%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20were%20not%20reflecting%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAir%20pollution%20in%20Delhi%20and%20NCR%20has%20become%20an%20annual%20ritual.%20Despite%20the%20directions%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20the%20appropriate%20governments%2C%20both%20central%20and%20states%2C%20have%20failed%20to%20coordinate%20and%20comply%2C%20thus%20making%20the%20problem%20a%20recurring%20nightmare%20for%20the%20citizens.%20Continued%20failure%20of%20executive%20to%20effectively%20discharge%20its%20responsibilities%20have%20put%20the%20onus%20on%20judiciary%20which%20has%20continuously%20been%20expressing%20its%20displeasure%20at%20the%20ineffectiveness%20of%20the%20governments%20in%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Suraj%20Kumar%2C%20advocate%2C%20Delhi%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20efforts%20in%20the%20past%20to%20devise%20an%20action%20plan%2C%20nothing%20seems%20to%20be%20moving%20on%20the%20ground.%20A%20three-judge%20Supreme%20Court%20bench%20shared%20the%20sentiment%20and%20observed%2C%20%26quot%3BStatistics%20at%20times%20can%20be%20deceptive...All%20these%20steps%20are%20only%20on%20paper.%20We%20have%20to%20see%20what%20the%20ground%20reality%20is.%20What%20is%20the%20impact%20of%20these%20steps%20if%20the%20air%20quality%20does%20not%20improve%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20always%2C%20the%20courts%20seem%20to%20be%20the%20sole%20saviour.%20The%20judgment%20will%20come%20in%20time.%20The%20execution%2C%20however%2C%20may%20again%20defy%20any%20time%20limit.%20Someone%20should%20be%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E(Bharti%20Mishra%20Nath%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist).%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699272780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fdp51n7_delhi-pollution-pti_625x300_06_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fit-is-delhis-annual-pollution-seas