%20booth%20on%20Tuesday%20allowing%20villagers%20to%20vote%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20their%20own%20village.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98My%20whole%20youth%20has%20been%20wasted%20in%20jail%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChandameta%20saw%20a%20massive%20security%20crackdown%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20killing%20of%20Congress%20leader%20Mahendra%20Karma%20in%20a%20Naxal%20attack%20in%202013%20in%20nearby%20Jhiram%20Ghati%20in%20Sukma%2C%20which%20wiped%20out%20the%20entire%20top%20state%20leadership%20of%20the%20party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESori%20was%20arrested%20in%20January%202014%20from%20the%20local%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebazaar%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eand%20the%20police%20suddenly%20turned%20up%20there%20and%20arrested%20me%20and%20claimed%20that%20I%20was%20helping%20Naxalis%20as%20an%20informer.%20I%20was%20doing%20no%20such%20thing%20but%20they%20did%20not%20listen%20to%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20terms%20%E2%80%98Naxali%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Naxal%E2%80%99%20are%20used%20interchangeably%20to%20mean%20%E2%80%98Maoists%E2%80%99%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20case%20dragged%20on%20for%20years%20in%20court%20as%20witnesses%2C%20who%20he%20said%20were%20largely%20villagers%20from%20Chindgur%20and%20police%20officials%2C%20rarely%20turned%20up%20to%20provide%20any%20evidence%20of%20his%20involvement%20with%20Maoists%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20was%20Naxali%20then%20something%20would%20come%20out%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%20But%20nothing%20ever%20came%20out%20and%20finally%20the%20case%20was%20dismissed%20and%20I%20was%20released%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Sori%20went%20to%20jail%20his%20daughter%20was%20just%20born.%20Nine%20years%20on%2C%20Sori%20has%20met%20his%20daughter%20twice%20after%20being%20released%20from%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20332px)%2085vw%2C%20332px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22332%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164937%2FShyam-Kavasi-who-left-Chandameta-for-nine-years-with-his-family-out-of-fear-of-the-naxals-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683742%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShyam%20Kavasi%20who%20left%20Chandameta%20for%20nine%20years%20with%20his%20family%20out%20of%20fear%20of%20Maoists.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20whole%20youth%20has%20been%20wasted%20in%20jail.%20Now%20I%20want%20to%20work%20hard%20on%20my%20farm%20to%20educate%20my%20daughter.%20This%20is%20like%20a%20new%20birth%20for%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20what%20he%20feels%20about%20the%20prospect%20of%20having%20a%20polling%20booth%20in%20his%20own%20village%2C%20Sori%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%20they%20(police%20and%20security%20forces)%20would%20look%20at%20us%20with%20suspicion%2C%20now%20they%20are%20urging%20us%20to%20go%20and%20vote.%20What%20can%20I%20say%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EA%20shadow%20on%20Chandameta%E2%80%99s%20development%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Sori%20has%20been%20released%2C%20about%2010%20other%20villagers%20who%20were%20arrested%20on%20suspicion%20of%20being%20aids%20to%20the%20Maoists%20like%20him%2C%20are%20still%20lodged%20in%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20those%20who%20are%20still%20in%20jail%20to%20be%20released%20as%20early%20as%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2021-year-old%20Shyam%20Kavasi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavasi%20said%20that%20his%20family%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20village%20for%20nine%20years%20at%20the%20height%20of%20Maoist%20activities%20in%20the%20area%20and%20only%20returned%20to%20the%20village%20two%20years%20ago%20when%20a%20CRPF%20camp%20was%20set%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20left%20out%20of%20fear.%20Even%20if%20we%20had%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bazaar%20we%20had%20to%20get%20their%20permission.%20If%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20permission%20they%20would%20accuse%20us%20of%20going%20to%20meet%20the%20police%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavasi%20and%20four%20others%20are%20the%20only%20ones%20in%20the%20village%20who%20have%20studied%20till%20Class%2012.%20With%20basic%20amenities%20now%20available%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Kavasi%20said%20that%20he%20wants%20his%20village%20to%20develop%20like%20other%20areas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CElectricity%20has%20just%20come%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20month%20but%20not%20to%20the%20entire%20village%20yet.%20One%20para%20still%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20electricity.%20When%20we%20see%20other%20villages%20they%20are%20well%20developed%2C%20we%20also%20want%20our%20village%20to%20be%20developed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20had%20developed%20our%20village%20earlier%20then%20this%20place%20would%20not%20have%20become%20Naxal%20dominated.%20Several%20villagers%20have%20been%20killed.%20Many%20villagers%20would%20see%20police%20and%20run%20away%20and%20the%20police%20would%20shoot%20them%20out%20of%20suspicion.%20I%20know%20of%20at%20least%20two%20such%20cases.%20The%20villagers%20have%20lost%20out%20between%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20security%20forces%20and%20the%20Maoists.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHarish%20Mandavi%2C%2021%2C%20says%20that%20villagers%20often%20did%20not%20have%20any%20option%20but%20to%20help%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20would%20come%20and%20point%20a%20gun%20to%20our%20heads%20and%20ask%20us%20for%20rice%2C%20dal%20and%20other%20rations%20or%20to%20cook%20food%20for%20them.%20We%20had%20no%20option%20but%20to%20do%20as%20they%20said%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMandavi%20who%20has%20studied%20till%20Class%205%20say%20that%20his%20father%20left%20him%20and%20his%20mother%20and%20two%20sisters%20in%202013.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20did%20not%20want%20to%20live%20under%20this%20kind%20of%20pressure%20anymore.%20But%20I%20never%20thought%20of%20leaving%20this%20village.%20I%20always%20thought%20that%20if%20I%20have%20to%20die%20then%20I%20will%20die%20here%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeveral%20villagers%20in%20Chandameta%20are%20still%20involved%20with%20Maoists%2C%20say%20current%20residents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavasi%20said%20that%20the%20Maoists%20would%20hold%20political%20discussions%20in%20the%20village%20and%20convince%20the%20villagers%20about%20not%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20just%20like%20political%20parties%20hold%20rallies%20in%20which%20they%20give%20speeches%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20government%20had%20brought%20development%20earlier%20then%20maybe%20Naxals%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20be%20so%20entrenched%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06165057%2FVoter-information-painted-on-Chandametas-first-polling-booth.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06165057%2FVoter-information-painted-on-Chandametas-first-polling-booth.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06165057%2FVoter-information-painted-on-Chandametas-first-polling-booth-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06165057%2FVoter-information-painted-on-Chandametas-first-polling-booth-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683748%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EInformation%20for%20voters%20on%20Chandameta%E2%80%99s%20first%20polling%20booth.%20Photo%3A%20Sravasti%20Dasgupta%2FThe%20Wire%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBasic%20amenities%20of%20development%20came%20to%20Chandameta%20only%20after%20a%20CRPF%20camp%20was%20set%20up%20in%20the%20village%20about%20two%20years%20ago.%20Maoist%20influence%20in%20the%20village%20has%20also%20receded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERaju%20Wagh%2C%20assistant%20commandant%2C%20CRPF%2C%20who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20camp%20in%20Chandameta%20said%20that%20it%20was%20not%20easy%20for%20the%20villagers%20to%20trust%20the%20security%20forces%20when%20the%20camp%20was%20just%20set%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20built%20trust%20over%20time%20and%20made%20them%20understand%20that%20we%20are%20here%20to%20help%20them.%20When%20we%20had%20just%20started%20they%20would%20see%20us%20and%20run%20away%20because%20they%20were%20scared.%20We%20started%20by%20teaching%20the%20village%20children%20in%20a%20tent%20near%20the%20camp.%20We%20participated%20in%20their%20festivals%2C%20pujas%2C%20held%20discussions%2C%20and%20invited%20them%20to%20Diwali%20celebrations%20in%20the%20camp.%20We%20distributed%20soaps%20and%20clothes%20and%20blankets.%20If%20anyone%20fell%20ill%20and%20needed%20hospital%20care%20we%20would%20send%20them%20to%20the%20nearby%20hospitals.%20None%20of%20them%20had%20Aadhaar%20cards%20or%20voter%20ID%20cards.%20We%20got%20that%20done%20as%20well.%20It%20has%20taken%20time%20but%20now%20the%20villagers%20have%20come%20to%20trust%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVillagers%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20say%20they%20are%20keen%20to%20work%20with%20the%20security%20forces.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlong%20with%20other%20youth%20in%20the%20village%2C%20Kavasi%20is%20trying%20to%20organise%20the%20villagers%20as%20a%20collective%20to%20bring%20more%20development%20to%20the%20village.%20Government%20officials%20including%20the%20Jagdalpur%20collector%20have%20visited%20the%20village%20a%20few%20times%20recently%20and%20promised%20to%20listen%20to%20their%20demands.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20trying%20to%20bring%20everyone%20together%20so%20we%20can%20make%20more%20demands%20to%20the%20government%20and%20bring%20more%20developmental%20work%20here.%20Development%20has%20come%20so%20suddenly%20here%20with%20roads%2C%20electricity%20that%20villagers%20themselves%20cannot%20understand%20how%20these%20things%20have%20happened%20in%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kavasi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699270153000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06164948%2FElectricity-lines-in-Chandameta-village.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-in-chandameta-with-electricity-roads-and-water-a-polling-booth-for-the-first-time%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Earlier%20villagers%20in%20Chandameta%20had%20to%20walk%20about%206%20kilometres%20to%20Chindgur%20to%20cast%20their%20votes.%20As%20many%20as%20337%20voters%20are%20scheduled%20to%20vote%20in%20the%20village%20on%20Tuesday.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchhattisgarh-in-chandameta-with-electricity-roads-and-water-a-polling-booth-for-the-first-time%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Days%20After%20157%20Killed%20In%20Strong%20Earthquake%2C%20Another%20One%20Hits%20Nepal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENepal%20was%20hit%20by%20a%205.6%20magnitude%20earthquake%20today%2C%20days%20after%20157%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20dozens%20injured%20when%20a%20strong%20quake%20struck%20the%20Himalayan%20country.%20The%20tremors%20were%20felt%20in%20neighbouring%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20earthquake%20this%20week%20occurred%20on%20Friday%20with%20a%20magnitude%206.4%2C%20Nepal's%20National%20Seismological%20Centre%20said.%20The%20German%20Research%20Centre%20for%20Geosciences%20measured%20the%20quake%20at%205.7%2C%20downgrading%20it%20from%206.2%2C%20while%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20pegged%20it%20at%205.6.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20count%20in%20Friday's%20earthquake%20in%20Jajarkot%20could%20rise%2C%20officials%20feared%2C%20as%20they%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20establish%20contact%20in%20the%20hilly%20area%20near%20the%20epicentre%2C%20some%20500%20km%20(300%20miles)%20west%20of%20the%20capital%20Kathmandu%2C%20where%20tremors%20were%20also%20felt.%20The%20district%20has%20a%20population%20of%20190%2C000%20with%20villages%20scattered%20in%20remote%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20search%20and%20rescue%20operation%20was%20also%20blocked%20by%20landslides%2C%20triggered%20by%20the%20earthquake%2C%20which%20hit%20the%20roads%20to%20reach%20the%20affected%20areas%2C%20Nepal%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20quake%2C%20thousands%20of%20buildings%20in%20Jajarkot%20and%20neighbouring%20Rukum%20West%20district%20have%20collapsed%20or%20developed%20cracks%20making%20them%20uninhabitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESurvivors%20said%20they%20heard%20the%20loud%20noises%20of%20collapsing%20buildings%20soon%20after%20the%20quake%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocal%20media%20footage%20showed%20crumbled%20facades%20of%20multi-storied%20brick%20houses%2C%20with%20large%20pieces%20of%20furniture%20scattered.%20Videos%20on%20X%20showed%20people%20running%20into%20the%20street%20as%20some%20buildings%20were%20evacuated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20earthquake%20was%20the%20deadliest%20since%202015%20when%20about%209%2C000%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20two%20earthquakes%20in%20Nepal.%20Whole%20towns%2C%20centuries-old%20temples%20and%20other%20historic%20sites%20were%20reduced%20to%20rubble%20then%2C%20with%20more%20than%20a%20million%20houses%20destroyed%2C%20at%20a%20cost%20to%20the%20economy%20of%20%246%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699270020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fiaqmgucs_nepal-earthquake-reuters_625x300_06_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdays-after-157-killed-in-strong-earthquake-another-one-hits-nepal-4550354%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nepal%20was%20hit%20by%20a%205.6%20magnitude%20earthquake%20today%2C%20days%20after%20157%20people%20were%20killed%20and%20dozens%20injured%20when%20a%20strong%20quake%20struck%20the%20Himalayan%20country.%20The%20tremors%20were%20felt%20in%20neighbouring%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdays-after-157-killed-in-strong-earthquake-another-one-hits-nepal-4550354%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdays-after-157-killed-in-strong-earthquake-another-one-hits-nepal-4550354%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdays-after-157-killed-in-strong-earthquake-another-one-hits-nepal-4550354%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Strong%20Tremors%20In%20Delhi%20After%205.6%20Magnitude%20Earthquake%20In%20Nepal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStrong%20tremors%20were%20felt%20in%20Delhi%20and%20nearby%20cities%20on%20Monday%20afternoon%20as%20a%205.6%20magnitude%20earthquake%20struck%20Nepal%20again%2C%20its%20second%20quake%20in%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Centre%20for%20Seismology%20said%20the%20epicentre%20for%20the%20quake%20was%20233%20kilometres%20north%20of%20Ayodhya%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tremors%20triggered%20panic%20among%20people%2C%20with%20many%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20reporting%20a%20vigorous%20shaking%20of%20desks%20and%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFootage%20on%20social%20media%20also%20showed%20people%20rushing%20out%20of%20residential%20buildings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELast%20Friday%2C%20a%20powerful%206.4%20earthquake%20hit%20Nepal%20that%20killed%20at%20least%20157%20people.%20It%20was%20the%20Himalayan%20nation's%20worst%20earthquake%20since%202015.%20Nepal%20lies%20in%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20active%20tectonic%20zones%20which%20makes%20it%20extremely%20vulnerable%20to%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699269300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Fudvi1s9g_india-gate-crowd-pti_625x300_25_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fearthquake-tremors-felt-in-delhi-neig