be%20part%20of%20my%20rich%2C%20diverse%20country%2C%20and%2C%20equally%2C%20part%20of%20the%20fascinating%2C%20complex%20larger%20world.%20All%20I%20need%20to%20do%20is%20fight%20for%20a%20better%20world%20for%20all.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20312px)%2085vw%2C%20312px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06130239%2F20231011_prabir_purkayastha_good_fight_cover_front-194x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22312%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06130239%2F20231011_prabir_purkayastha_good_fight_cover_front-194x300.jpg%20194w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06130239%2F20231011_prabir_purkayastha_good_fight_cover_front-662x1024.jpg%20662w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06130239%2F20231011_prabir_purkayastha_good_fight_cover_front.jpg%20776w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683676%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22482%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPrabir%20Purkayastha%3Cbr%3E%3Cem%3EKeeping%20Up%20the%20Good%20Fight%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3ELeftWord%20Books%20(October%202023)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20fight%20and%20arrest%20this%20time%2C%20mirrors%20his%20arrest%20and%20%E2%80%9Cdaylight%20kidnapping%E2%80%9D%20in%201975%20during%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Emergency.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20on%20the%20lawns%20of%20the%20School%20of%20Languages%20that%20morning%2C%20with%20a%20few%20friends%20from%20the%20Students%E2%80%99%20Federation%20of%20India%20(SFI)%2C%20when%20a%20black%20ambassador%20stopped%20near%20us%20and%20a%20burly%20man%20got%20out.%20He%20came%20up%20to%20me%20and%20asked%20if%20I%20was%20D.P.%20Tripathi%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%93%3C%2Fem%3E%20then%20president%20of%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20union.%20I%20replied%20that%20I%20was%20not%2C%20but%20my%20questioner%20was%20a%20cop%2C%20DIG%20Range%20P.S.%20Bhinder%2C%20and%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20believe%20me.%20He%20and%20his%20men%2C%20all%20in%20plainclothes%2C%20swiftly%20proceeded%20to%20kidnap%20me%20in%20broad%20daylight.%20I%20would%20end%20up%20in%20jail%2C%20%5Bwas%5D%20kept%20there%20for%20a%20year%20under%20the%20Maintenance%20of%20Internal%20Security%20Act%20(MISA)%2C%E2%80%9D%20Purkayastha%20recounted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20telling%20how%20long%20his%20incarceration%20will%20last%20this%20time.%20But%20Purkayastha%20is%20one%20of%20those%20for%20whom%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20real%20question%20is%20about%20the%20side%20of%20history%20you%20are%20on.%E2%80%9D%20And%20he%20believes%20that%20when%20he%20looks%20back%2C%20to%20the%201975%20Emergency%20or%20at%20the%20one%20today%2C%20he%20does%20not%20not%20want%20to%20look%20at%20it%20from%20the%20point%20of%20view%20of%20a%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CVictimhood%20robs%20us%20of%20participation%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20history%3B%20it%20reduces%20us%20to%20mere%20objects%20of%20history.%20Instead%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20assume%20the%20vantage%20point%20of%20people%20as%20makers%20of%20history.%20Yes%2C%20the%20government%20of%20the%20day%20wields%20powers%20that%20seem%20to%20overwhelm%20individuals%20and%20organisations.%20But%20it%20is%20people%2C%20and%20their%20actions%2C%20that%20finally%20determine%20history%3B%20not%20as%20we%20please%20and%20when%20we%20please%2C%20but%20in%20ways%20that%20neither%20the%20people%20nor%20their%20rulers%20anticipate.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20slim%20200-odd%20pages%20of%20this%20modern%20masterpiece%2C%20Purkayastha%20weaves%20in%20his%20own%20personal%20story%20with%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20story%20of%20standing%20up%20to%20overbearing%20authority%20figures.%20Written%20in%20lucid%20prose%2C%20this%20autobiography%20is%20not%20an%20exercise%20in%20self-glorification%20or%20a%20boring%20story%20boringly%20told.%20It%20is%20a%20fighter%E2%80%99s%20examination%20of%20his%20own%20life%20and%20the%20people%20who%20shaped%20it.%20It%20is%20told%20without%20malice%20or%20rancour.%20Even%20those%20who%20have%20mistreated%20him%20are%20not%20made%20villains%20of%20choice%20but%20creatures%20of%20circumstance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fdifference-then-and-now-prabir-purkayastha-book-excerpt%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98The%20Difference%20Between%20Then%20and%20Now%E2%80%99%3A%20Prabir%20Purkayastha%20on%20Emergency%20and%20the%20Modi%20Years%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPurkayastha%20is%20an%20engineer%2C%20a%20man%20of%20science%2C%20who%20has%20made%20a%20conscious%20choice%20in%20his%20politics%20and%20lived%20by%20that%20logic.%20He%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20several%20milestones%20along%20the%20way%2C%20but%20the%20most%20important%20one%20was%20the%20discovery%20that%20I%20had%20three%20%E2%80%98passions%E2%80%99%20I%20would%20always%20live%20with%3A%20science%2C%20technology%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20politics.%20How%20these%20three%20would%20come%20together%20over%20the%20next%20four%20(and%20more)%20decades%20became%20clearer%20only%20with%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20begins%20with%20a%20chapter%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%98Does%20Every%20Generation%20Have%20to%20Face%20an%20Emergency%3F%E2%80%99.%20It%20then%20segues%20into%20the%20author%E2%80%99s%20personal%20journey%20in%20subsequent%20chapters%20called%2C%20%E2%80%98Learning%20to%20Fight%3A%20A%20Personal%20Journey%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98To%20Delhi%20and%20a%20Turning%20Point%E2%80%99.%20The%20next%20two%20chapters%20%E2%80%93%20titled%20%E2%80%98A%20University%20Under%20Emergency%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Life%20in%20Jail%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20cover%20his%20recollections%20of%20the%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20in%20the%2070s%20and%20his%20experience%20in%20prison.%20The%20book%20then%20looks%20at%20%E2%80%98The%20Last%20Chapter%20of%20Mrs%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Emergency%E2%80%99%20before%20recording%20the%20major%20portion%20of%20his%20working%20life%20in%20%E2%80%98Living%20Politics%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F14115727%2FPrabir-Newsclick.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22750%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F14115727%2FPrabir-Newsclick.jpg%20750w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F14115727%2FPrabir-Newsclick-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-509808%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20owner%20and%20editor%20Prabir%20Purkayastha.%20Photo%3A%20YouTube%20screengrab%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20take%20people%E2%80%99s%20silence%20for%20assent%3A%20This%20was%20the%20crucial%20lesson%20of%20the%20Emergency%20for%20our%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Purkayastha%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20%E2%80%9CMrs%20Gandhi%20knew%20that%20she%20needed%20the%20affirmation%20of%20the%20people%20through%20an%20election%20that%20was%20truly%20free.%20The%20current%20dispensation%20believes%20that%20the%20facade%20of%20freedom%2C%20combined%20with%20control%20over%20media%2C%20including%20social%20media%2C%20is%20enough.%20Yes%2C%20it%20may%20be%20possible%20to%20do%20this%20for%20a%20short%20time%2C%20maybe%20in%20a%20few%20states%2C%20often%20by%20creating%20warlike%20conditions%20with%20a%20neighbour%2C%20and%2C%20throughout%2C%20appealing%20to%20people%20to%20close%20ranks%20behind%20the%20great%20leader.%20But%20not%20for%20long%2C%20not%20across%20the%20country.%20As%20Shelley%E2%80%99s%20immortal%20line%20says%3A%20%E2%80%98Ye%20are%20many%2C%20they%20are%20few%E2%80%99!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20that%20this%20book%20had%20been%20released%20before%20his%20arrest%20and%20the%20orchestrated%20media%20campaign%20about%20Purkayastha%20and%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20links%20to%20China%20through%20American%20businessman%20Neville%20Roy%20Singham.%20Purkayastha%20states%20in%20chapter%207%2C%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6Later%2C%20while%20I%20worked%20as%20a%20consultant%20with%20Steag%2C%20I%20set%20up%20a%20small%20news%20portal%2C%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20in%202009.%20I%20would%20commute%20every%20day%20from%20Gurgaon%2C%20where%20I%20lived%2C%20to%20the%20office%20at%20Noida%2C%20and%20to%20Malviya%20Nagar%20in%20the%20evening%20to%20%3Cem%3ENewsClick%3C%2Fem%3E%20before%20returning%20to%20Gurgaon%20late%20at%20night.%20Later%2C%20I%20joined%20the%20software%20company%20Thoughtworks%2C%20then%20owned%20by%20the%20tech%20wiz%20Singham%2C%20in%202013%2C%20and%20worked%20there%20as%20a%20consultant%20till%202017%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20events%20in%20the%20course%20of%20his%20life%20occurred%20before%20the%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Esamvat%3C%2Fem%3E%20(era)%20began%20in%20May%202014.%20The%20entire%20case%20against%20Purkayastha%20today%20seems%20to%20be%20as%20insubstantial%20as%20the%20one%20in%201975.%20I%20do%20hope%20that%20someone%20in%20authority%20pays%20attention%20and%20releases%20the%20man%20who%20has%20always%20fought%20the%20good%20fight.%20If%20not%2C%20this%20book%20will%20stand%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20his%20times%20and%20ours.%20The%20book%20rewards%20the%20reader%20in%20so%20many%20ways%20and%20I%20do%20hope%20that%20it%20is%20translated%20into%20all%20major%20languages%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fsanjay-hegde%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Hegde%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20advocate%2C%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699268423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F06131557%2FScreenshot-2023-11-06-at-1.15.11%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fprabir-purkayasthas-autobiography-marks-his-journey-from-one-emergency-to-another%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20slim%20200-odd%20pages%20of%20this%20modern%20masterpiece%2C%20Purkayastha%20weaves%20his%20own%20personal%20story%20with%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20story%20of%20standing%20up%20to%20overbearing%20authority%20figures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fprabir-purkayasthas-autobiography-marks-his-journey-from-one-emergency-to-another%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Is%20Timed%20Out%20Law%3F%20Explaining%20Angelo%20Mathews'%20World%20Cup%20Dismissal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%C2%A0Sri%20Lanka%20all-rounder%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Angelo%20Mathews%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1260-angelo-mathews-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAngelo%20Mathews%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20dismissed%20in%20a%20bizarre%20manner%2C%20having%20failed%20to%20make%20it%20to%20the%20pitch%20on%20time%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%20match%20against%20Bangladesh.%20According%20to%20the%20timed-out%20rule%2C%20the%20batter%20has%20to%20make%20the%20pitch%20within%203%20minutes%20(2%20minutes%20in%20World%20Cups)%20of%20the%20dismissal%20of%20the%20previous%20player%20and%20be%20ready%20to%20face%20the%20next%20delivery.%20While%20Mathews%20had%20entered%20the%20ground%2C%20he%20encountered%20some%20issues%20with%20his%20helmet%2C%20which%20required%20him%20to%20call%20for%20a%20replacement.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20the%20maximum%20allowed%20time%20had%20already%20passed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBangladesh%20skipper%20Shakib%20Al%20Has%20decided%20to%20appeal%2C%20and%20according%20to%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20officials%20had%20to%20give%20Mathews%20out.%20In%20the%20process%2C%20Mathews%20had%20to%20depart%20without%20facing%20a%20single%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EHISTORY%20IN%20DELHI....!!!%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20Angelo%20Mathews%20becomes%20the%20first%20cricketer%20in%20history%20to%20be%20out%20on%20'timed%20out'.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FVRg1xmSTDf%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FVRg1xmSTDf%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%E2%80%94%20Mufaddal%20Vohra%20(%40mufaddal_vohra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmufaddal_vohra%2Fstatus%2F1721474780355059770%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%206%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20the%20rule%20book%20say%20on%20Time%20Out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERule%2040.1.1%20states%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20the%20fall%20of%20a%20wicket%20or%20the%20retirement%20of%20a%20batter%2C%20the%20incoming%20batter%20must%2C%20unless%20Time%20has%20been%20called%2C%20be%20ready%20to%20receive%20the%20ball%2C%20or%20for%20the%20other%20batter%20to%20be%20ready%20to%20receive%20the%20next%20ball%20within%203%20minutes%20of%20the%20dismissal%20or%20retirement.%20If%20this%20requirement%20is%20not%20met%2C%20the%20incoming%20batter%20will%20be%20out%2C%20Timed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20per%20rule%2040.1.2%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20event%20of%20an%20extended%20delay%20in%20which%20no%20batter%20comes%20to%20the%20wicket%2C%20the%20umpires%20shall%20adopt%20the%20procedure%20of%20Law%2016.3%20(Umpires%20awarding%20a%20match).%C2%A0%C2%A0For%20the%20purposes%20of%20that%20Law%20the%20start%20of%20the%20action%20shall%20be%20taken%20as%20the%20expiry%20of%20the%203%20minutes%20referred%20to%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20to%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20bowler%20doesn't%20get%20credit%20for%20this%20dismissal%2C%