struggle-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efirst%20love%20of%20photography%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%20in%201948%2C%20when%20a%20vacancy%20opened%20up%20for%20a%20staff%20photographer%20at%20the%20newly%20launched%20Deccan%20Herald%20%E2%80%94%20an%20English%20daily%20based%20in%20Karnataka%20%E2%80%94%20Satyan%20grabbed%20the%20opportunity.%20This%20was%20his%20first%20professional%20stint%20with%20a%20camera%20and%20he%20delivered%20to%20impress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201445px)%20100vw%2C%201445px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221445%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22T%20S%20Satyan%20was%20known%20for%20his%20trademark%20black%20and%20white%20pictures%20that%20captured%20the%20mood%20of%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197.jpg%201445w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-212x300.jpg%20212w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-500x709.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-768x1088.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-1084x1536.jpg%201084w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2Flicensed-image_11zon-1699013197-150x213.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333534%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ET%20S%20Satyan%20was%20known%20for%20his%20trademark%20black%20and%20white%20pictures%20that%20captured%20the%20mood%20of%20India%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Wikipedia%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20trademark%20black-and-white%20pictures%20chronicled%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20mood.%20Satyan%20made%20his%20mark%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20earliest%20photojournalists%20at%20a%20time%20when%20photography%20was%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F296104%2Findia-first-selfie-by-maharaja-bir-chandra-of-tripura%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elimited%20to%20portraits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Since%20his%20assignment%20in%20the%20Deccan%20Herald%2C%20Satyan%20spent%20the%20next%2060%20years%20documenting%20both%20the%20momentous%20and%20regular%20moments%20in%20Indian%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20certain%20magic%20to%20the%20pictures%20he%20captured%20as%20if%20stealing%20a%20moment%20in%20time%20from%20his%20subject%E2%80%99s%20life.%20As%20he%20once%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20photography%20are%20slices%20of%20human%20life%2C%20gentle%20and%20personal.%20Their%20aim%20is%20to%20let%20the%20viewer%20see%20all%20by%20himself.%20They%20tend%20not%20to%20preach%2C%20not%20to%20pose%20as%20art.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%20always%20emphasised%20that%20his%20pictures%20were%20not%20the%20result%20of%20encounters%20between%20events%20and%20him%20but%20rather%20a%20witness%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F290133%2Fkerala-photographer-sharun-recreates-raja-ravi-varma-paintings-with-trans-models%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteresting%20moments%20in%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20people%20he%20met.%20%E2%80%9CPhotography%20has%20enabled%20me%20to%20save%20them%20from%20vanishing%20into%20thin%20air%20and%20to%20give%20them%20a%20life%20of%20their%20own.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20many%20iconic%20moments%20he%20covered%20were%20the%20merger%20of%20Pondicherry%20with%20the%20Union%20of%20India%20in%201954%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ESatyagraha%3C%2Fem%3E%20against%20Portuguese%20rule%20in%20Goa%20during%20the%201950s%2C%20Pope%20Paul%20VI%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20India%20in%201964%2C%20and%20the%20smallpox%20eradication%20campaign%20organised%20by%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20between%201961%E2%80%9363.%20In%201977%2C%20he%20was%20awarded%20the%20Padma%20Shri%20for%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F283077%2Fwoman-quits-law-labour-child-birth-photography-unconventional-jobs-mommy-story%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiconic%20events%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20iconic%20people%20too%20were%20part%20of%20Satyan%E2%80%99s%20subjects%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Nobel%20laureate%20C%20V%20Raman%2C%20filmmaker%20Satyajit%20Ray%2C%20Pt%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%2C%20the%20Dalai%20Lama%2C%20and%20Pope%20Paul%20VI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20maintained%20till%20the%20last%20that%20amidst%20the%20honours%20and%20accolades%2C%20his%20expertise%20lay%20in%20capturing%20the%20ordinary%20moments%20and%20the%20mundanity%20of%20routine%20life.%20From%20weddings%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20and%20polling%20booths%20in%20the%201970s%20to%20surgical%20procedures%20at%20AIIMS%20Delhi%20and%20Bangladesh%20refugees%2C%20Satyan%20captured%20it%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20recalled%20in%20an%20interview%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20people%20are%20not%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20famous.%20They%20are%20the%20simple%2C%20ordinary%20folk.%20They%20do%20not%20hit%20the%20headlines%2C%20yet%20my%20people%20are%20people%20who%20matter.%20They%20were%20there%20when%20I%20picked%20up%20the%20camera%20six%20decades%20ago%2C%20and%20they%20have%20been%20there%20every%20time%20I%20have%20gone%20back%20to%20capture%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F262805%2Fdorje-angchuk-ladakh-night-stars-galaxy-sky-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteresting%20moments%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20their%20lives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20photography%20made%20waves%2C%20his%20words%20did%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%E2%80%99s%20memoir%20%E2%80%98Alive%20and%20Clicking%E2%80%99%20published%20in%202005%20tells%20the%20story%20of%20the%20days%20he%20spent%20in%20Afghanistan%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Sikkim%20amongst%20others%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F260630%2Fphoto-journalist-viral-retirement-travel-tokyo-olympics-sachin-tendulkar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrief%20encounters%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20led%20to%20some%20of%20his%20best%20work.%20As%20he%20writes%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20you%20spend%20eighty%20summers%20on%20one%20planet%20with%20a%20camera%20in%20hand%2C%20things%20happen%2C%20events%20occur%2C%20and%20you%20have%20a%20bunch%20of%20experiences%20and%20encounters%20because%20you%20were%20there%20at%20the%20right%20time%20at%20the%20right%20place.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatyan%20passed%20away%20in%202009%20in%20Mysore%20but%20not%20before%20leaving%20behind%20a%20legacy%20of%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20look%20at%20it%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201500px)%20100vw%2C%201500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08_PHY.10165-1_11zon-1699013606.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Flash%20Floods%2C%20Delhi%2C%201970%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08_PHY.10165-1_11zon-1699013606.jpg%201500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08_PHY.10165-1_11zon-1699013606-300x204.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F08_PHY.10165-1_11zon-1699013606-500x340.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co