%2C%20reflecting%20the%20essence%20of%20ordinary%20people.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333532%2Fpadma-shri-t-s-satyan-father-of-indian-photojournalism-mysuru-bengaluru-history-pictures%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explore%20a%20New%20Side%20of%20Bengaluru%20Through%20This%20Storyteller%E2%80%99s%20Unique%20%E2%80%98Bangalore%20Walks%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThink%20of%20the%20game%20Monopoly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Arun%20Pai%20%E2%80%94%20the%20man%20behind%20%E2%80%98Bangalore%20Walks%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20urges%20me%2C%20attempting%20to%20explain%20where%20the%20idea%20for%20this%20unique%20experience%20stemmed%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20corporate%20executive-turned-storyteller%20made%20it%20clear%20from%20the%20start%20that%20he%20never%20planned%20to%20conduct%20the%20%E2%80%9Cregular%E2%80%9D%20heritage%20walks.%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20do%20is%20tell%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304974%2Fbest-vintage-stays-heritage-bungalows-hotels-and-homestays-in-kolkata%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estory%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Pai%2C%20now%20in%20his%2050s.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202004%2C%20after%20a%20brief%207-year%20stint%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20Pai%20decided%20he%20wanted%20more%20from%20life%20than%20a%20corner%20cabin%20and%20its%20perks.%C2%A0%20During%20a%20business%20trip%20to%20London%2C%20he%20spent%20the%20major%20part%20of%20his%20days%20exploring%20the%20city%2C%20going%20on%20heritage%20walks%2C%20and%20wondering%20why%20India%20lacked%20these%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20returning%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20feeling%20of%20diving%20into%20something%20creative%20overtook%20him.%20He%20bade%20goodbye%20to%20the%20corporate%20world%20and%20started%20%E2%80%98Bangalore%20Walks%E2%80%99%2C%20literally%20and%20figuratively%20taking%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304444%2Foddar-community-keeps-thammampatti-tamil-nadu-art-alive-for-decades-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20road%20less%20travelled%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20these%20walks%20have%20given%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20metropolis%20as%20well%20as%20celebrated%20personalities%20a%20chance%20to%20fall%20in%20love%20with%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20unseen%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20early%20years%20of%20starting%2C%20Pai%20began%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20man%20who%20showed%20up%20every%20Sunday%20morning%20at%207%20on%20Bengaluru%E2%80%99s%20MG%20Road%20ready%20to%20begin%20his%20signature%20three-hour-long%20%E2%80%98Victorian%20Bangalore%20Walk%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECome%20rain%20or%20shine%2C%20this%20was%20a%20weekly%20ritual.%20And%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20turned%20up%20never%20deterred%20his%20spirit.%20%E2%80%9CSometimes%20it%20was%20a%20handful%2C%20other%20times%20a%20crowd.%E2%80%9D%20But%20Pai%20saw%20to%20it%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289457%2Findia-museums-travel-city-culture-history-must-visit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20show%20went%20o%3C%2Fa%3En.%20And%20today%2C%20he%20has%20taken%20over%2030%2C000%20people%20on%20more%20than%201%2C500%20heritage%20walks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20Indian%20history%20from%20textbooks%20to%20the%20world%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWith-G20-Culture-Summit_11zon-1698934986.jpg%5C%2