0Mayfair%2C%20Piccadilly%E2%80%A6these%20places%20were%20rooted%20in%20our%20memory.%20We%20could%20roll%20the%20dice%2C%20buy%20a%20property%2C%20and%20pay%20rent.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20didn%E2%80%99t%20realise%20how%20the%20game%20was%20impacting%20him%20until%20his%20first%20trip%20to%20London%20revealed%20how%20he%20knew%20the%20city%20like%20the%20back%20of%20his%20hand.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20simple%20game.%20It%20was%20designed%20with%20the%20intent%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256888%2Fprofessor-thirumallini-selvaraj-civil-engineer-restore-heritage-structure-sustainable-ancient-architecture-india-div200%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebringing%20the%20city%20alive%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20imagination%20of%20kids%20whose%20only%20source%20of%20information%20was%20these%20board%20games%20back%20in%20the%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20while%20London%20seemed%20so%20familiar%2C%20Delhi%20did%20not.%20And%20Pai%20is%20quick%20to%20note%20the%20reason.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20only%20place%20we%20have%20learnt%20Indian%20history%20is%20in%20textbooks.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20with%20a%20desire%20to%20tell%20India%E2%80%99s%20story%20to%20anyone%20who%20would%20listen%2C%20he%20started%20%E2%80%98Bangalore%20Walks%E2%80%99.%20While%20fleshing%20out%20the%20idea%20for%20this%20initiative%2C%20he%20was%20firm%20that%20his%20focus%20would%20not%20lie%20on%20museums%20and%20monuments.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F249996%2Fpunjab-best-food-amritsar-golden-temple-kesar-da-dhaba-nehru-lala-lajpat-rai-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEvery%20street%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20boasts%20a%20story%20and%20Pai%20would%20find%20it%20and%20tell%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20love%20affair%20wi