EWhile%20the%20walks%20do%20not%20have%20a%20set%20theme%2C%20Pai%20improvises%20along%20the%20way%20depending%20on%20the%20audience%20he%20is%20catering%20to.%20And%20he%20delivers%20every%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20model%20caters%20to%20specific%20groups%20as%20opposed%20to%20public%20walks.%20A%20group%20of%2025%20individuals%20from%20a%20policy%20think%20tank%20in%20the%20city%20who%20recently%20attended%20one%20of%20the%20walks%20will%20agree.%20After%20three%20hours%20spent%20covering%20what%20they%20thought%20were%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F185733%2Fkolkata-kumortuli-mud-sculptures-tradition-durga-puja-heritage-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamiliar%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20city%20centre%2C%20(near%20their%20office)%2C%20the%20group%20was%20enthralled%20by%20this%20new%20lens%20through%20which%20they%20were%20seeing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Pai%2C%20it%20was%20the%20same%20route%20he%20took%20with%20all%20his%20groups%2C%20but%20the%20storytelling%20differed.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20there%20were%20retired%20army%20personnel%20and%20defence%20strategists%20in%20the%20group%2C%20I%20ended%20up%20talking%20about%20the%20military%20DNA%20of%20Bangalore%20more%20than%20I%20would%20to%20a%20bunch%20of%20school%20children%20for%20whom%20that%20is%20not%20so%20exciting.%20So%20you%20see%2C%20the%20slant%20changes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F184025%2Fchennai-man-maritime-museum-lighthouse-heritage-inspiring-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efavourite%20stories%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20the%20walks%20is%20narrating%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cdramatic%E2%80%9D%20Battle%20of%20Bangalore%20that%20took%20place%20in%201791.%20After%20mortal%20combat%20with%20Tipu%20Sultan%E2%80%99s%20army%2C%20the%20Bangalore%20Fort%20was%20captured%2C%20leaving%20thousands%20of%20Mysoreans%20dead.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20know%20of%20the%20Battle%20of%20Panipat%20and%20Plassey%20but%20not%20this%20event%2C%20which%20had%20an%20equally%20large%20impact%20on%20India%2C%20if%20not%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pai.%20He%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20an%20interesting%20story%20of%20the%20role%20the%20fall%20of%20Bengaluru%20played%20in%20our%20history%2C%20and%20I%20tell%20it%20in%20such%20a%20fashion%20that%20people%20want%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20story%20picked%20up%20by%C2%A0%20Pai%20%E2%80%94%20the%20lores%20of%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20churches%2C%20the%20mapping%20of%20India%20that%20began%20in%20the%20city%20%E2%80%94%20has%20global%20appeal%20and%20is%20infused%20with%20personal%20anecdotes.%20Often%20in%20the%20course%20of%20the%20walk%2C%20Pai%20gets%20asked%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9CChristmas%20trees%E2%80%9D%20that%20line%20the%20roads.%20He%20then%20stops%20and%20narrates%20how%20they%20came%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDid%20you%20know%20they%20are%20actually%20from%20New%20Zealand%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asks%20me.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%2060-foot%20trees%20are%20so%20prevalent%20these%20days%20that%20most%20people%20think%20they%20are%20native%20to%20the%20city.%20But%20it%20is%20interesting%20to%20know%20that%20they%20were%20brought%20here%20almost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F182026%2Fmughal-miniatures-stunning-street-art-photo-story-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E200%20years%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20part%20of%20a%20massive%20botanical%20experiment%20by%20British%20and%20Indian%20scientists.%20They%20were%20trying%20to%20understand%20how%20to%20classify%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20trees%20and%20plants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20the%20city%20is%20not%20too%20high%2C%20not%20too%20low%2C%20not%20too%20wet%2C%20not%20too%20dry%2C%20it%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20conducive%20environment%20for%20these%20very%20foreign%20trees%20to%20grow.%20Today%20these%20%E2%80%98Christmas%20trees%E2%80%99%20(Norfolk%20Island%20Pines)%20have%20acclimatised%20to%20this%20climate%20and%20soil%20and%20have%20become%20local.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPai%20has%20narrated%20these%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F144331%2Fasi-finds-copper-bronze-age-chariots-tombs-up-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20stories%20of%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20some%20of%20the%20most%20influential%20people%20%E2%80%94%20including%20global%20MD%20of%20McKinsey%20Dominic%20Barton%2C%20president%20of%20Microsoft%20Brad%20Smith%2C%20Infosys%20founder%20NR%20Narayanamurthy%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20Chief%20Economic%20Advisor%20Anantha%20Nageswaran%2C%C2%A0US%20Digital%20Ambassador%20Nathaniel%20Fick%2C%20former%20PM%20of%20Australia%20Kevin%20Rudd%20and%20comedian%20Trevor%20Noah.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Nageswaran%20recounts%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20so%20happy%20that%20my%20friends%20from%20iSPIRT%20arranged%20for%20me%20to%20join%20Arun%20Pai%E2%80%99s%20Bengaluru%20walk%20on%2024%20July.%20He%20was%20simply%20brilliant%20with%20his%20erudition%2C%20wit%2C%20and%20deep%20understanding%20of%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%2C%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20city.%20His%20pride%20in%20being%20a%20Bangalorean%20came%20through%20so%20well%20that%20I%20was%20infected%20with%20that%20pride.%20He%20made%20Sir%20M%20Visweswaraiya%20and%20the%20Mysore%20Maharaja%20come%20alive%20with%20his%20vivid%20descriptions%20of%20their%20vision%20and%20their%20contributions%20to%20the%20city%20and%20the%20country.%20It%20was%20a%20perfect%20start%20to%20the%20day%20and%20made%20my%20short%20visit%20to%20Bengaluru%20entirely%20memorable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20adulation%2C%20one%20experience%20outshines%20it%20all%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Presidency%20of%20the%20G20%20Summit%20in%202023.%20Karnataka%20played%20host%20to%20over%2010%20important%20summit%20meetings%20over%20the%20year%20including%20the%20G20%20Summit.%20And%20Pai%20was%20the%20official%20representative%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20Karnataka%20for%20designing%20and%20planning%20the%20city%20tours%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F127339%2Fcalcutta-houses-instagram-photo-project%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexcursions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20last%20detail%20%E2%80%94%20including%20sites%20around%20cities%20like%20Mysuru%2C%20Hampi%2C%20and%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20experience%20at%20Hampi%2C%20Pai%20says%20it%20was%20phenomenal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20course%20of%20the%20three%20days%2C%20I%20highlighted%20globally%20relevant%20stories%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20history%2C%20culture%20and%20society%20to%20over%20200%20delegates%C2%A0from%2020%20countries.%20We%20were%20given%20a%20clear%20task%20by%20Amitabh%20Kant%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20Sherpa.%20He%20wanted%20us%20to%20provide%20the%20right%20context%2C%20background%20and%20experiences%20so%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F119531%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-kashmirs-famous-pashmina%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esplendour%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20scale%20and%20sagacity%20of%20the%20Vijayanagar%20Empire%20could%20be%20effectively%20communicated%20to%20the%20high-empowered%20global%20audience.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Pai%2C%20each%20walk%20is%20a%20creative%20utilisation%20of%20everything%20he%20has%20discovered%20about%20the%20city.%20He%20concludes%20by%20emphasising%20something%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20agree%20with%20more%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20not%20a%20heritage%20walker.%20I%20am%20India%E2%80%99s%20storyteller.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698999804000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2FWith-G20-Culture-Summit_11zon-1698934986.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333441%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bengaluru's%20Arun%20Pai%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job%20to%20start%20%E2%80%98Bangalore%20Walks%E2%80%99%20and%20use%20storytelling%20to%20showcase%20the%20history%20and%20heritage%20of%20prominent%20Indian%20cities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A124%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Worried%20About%20Parents%20Living%20Alone%3F%20These%20Safety%20Devices%20Bring%20Help%20to%20Elders%20in%20Minutes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20common%2C%20enduring%20trend%20in%20recent%20times%20is%20that%20of%20people%20having%20nuclear%20families%2C%20who%20often%20witness%20their%20children%20moving%20away%20in%20pursuit%20of%20better%20opportunities.%20This%2C%20however%2C%20leaves%20senior%20citizens%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F15-million-elderly-indians-live-all-alone-census%2Farticleshow%2F43948392.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecensus%20%3C%2Fa%3Edata%2C%20approximately%2015%20million%20senior%20citizens%20live%20alone%2C%20leaving%20them%20potentially%20exposed%20to%20unfavourable%20conditions%2C%20including%20loneliness.%20A%20recent%20survey%20conducted%20by%20the%20Delhi-based%20NGO%2C%20Agewell%20Foundation%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Fscience%2Fno-company-for-old-men-survey-finds-one-fourth-of-elderly-population-living-alone%2Farticleshow%2F64918809.cms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%2024.44%25%20of%20a%20sample%20of%2010%2C000%20elderly%20individuals%20lived%20in%20solitary%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20further%20revealed%20that%20%E2%80%9Calmost%20every%20second%20elderly%20person%20(48.88%25)%20lives%20alone%20in%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20situation%20expected%20to%20worsen%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20this%20issue%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F227280%2Fkerala-startup-malai-vegan-leather-coconut-water-biodegradable-sustainable-innovation-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKerala-based%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20up%20with%20affordable%20emergency-alert%20technology%20to%20assist%20senior%20citizens%20living%20in%20solitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFounded%20by%20Venunath%20V%20in%202021%2C%20Ansfrid%20SmartCare%20Pvt%20Ltd%20has%20launched%20nearly%20a%20dozen%20products%20to%20help%20the%20elderly%20live%20a%20safe%20and%20less%20vulnerable%20solitary%20life.%20In%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Venunath%20talks%20about%20his%20personal%20experience%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F323097%2Fpune-man-starts-yodda-elder-care-startup-for-emergency-help-to-senior-citizens%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelderly%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20technology%20and%20the%20products%20his%20company%20offers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98My%20mind%20needed%20the%20right%20nudge%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20school-going%20boy%2C%20all%20that%20Venunath%20dreamt%20of%20was%20to%20become%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20have%20a%20business%20that%20he%20could%20grow%20independently.%20Even%20at%20that%20young%20age%2C%20his%20mind%20wo