ses.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20earning%20some%20Rs%20500%20per%20sale%20which%20was%20a%20huge%20deal%20for%20me%20back%20then.%20However%2C%20as%20my%20parents%20kept%20on%20urging%20me%20to%20study%20hard%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20focus%20on%20that%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Venunath%20moved%20his%20priorities%20towards%20his%20education%2C%20he%20did%20not%20stop%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332063%2Fgujarat-first-trans-businesswoman-rajvi-jaan-jagruti-namkeen-vastu-puja-store-surat%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworking%20on%20his%20business.%3C%2Fa%3E%20In%20the%20span%20of%20five%20years%2C%20he%20grew%20the%20business%20while%20completing%20his%20schooling%20and%20graduation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20going%20well%20and%20I%20had%20a%20small%20team%20of%20software%20developers%20working%20with%20me.%20However%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20study%20more%20and%20open%20more%20avenues%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20In%202012%2C%20he%20moved%20to%20Sweden%20for%20his%20postgraduate%20studies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20move%20would%20eventually%20give%20Venunath%20the%20direction%20his%20innovative%20mind%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMaking%20the%20lives%20of%20solitary%20senior%20citizens%20safe%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20moved%20to%20Sweden%2C%20I%20had%20to%20look%20for%20accommodation%20as%20the%20college%20did%20not%20have%20any.%20I%20found%20a%20place%20with%20an%20elderly%20woman%20in%20a%20rural%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20lady%20lived%20alone%20and%20had%20sublet%20her%20apartment%20to%20Venunath.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20time%2C%20she%20was%20almost%2080%20years%20old%20and%20living%20with%20her%20made%20me%20realise%20how%20hard%20it%20can%20be%20to%20live%20alone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A