Fudaysinh-jadhav-ahmedabad-auto-rickshaw-driver-runs-on-gift-economy-pay-it-forward%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccident%20victims%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20their%20autos.%20Today%2C%20the%20autos%20serve%20as%20ambulances.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20an%20accident%20happens%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20wait%20for%20an%20ambulance%20or%20the%20Police%20to%20arrive.%20We%20rush%20the%20injured%20to%20the%20nearest%20hospital.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20have%20reduced%20the%20need%20for%20ambulances.%20We%20are%20available%20for%20any%20medical%20emergency%2C%20free%20of%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20they%20ferry%20people%20with%20disability%20free%20of%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20informs%20that%20any%20lost%20items%20in%20the%20auto%20are%20returned%20to%20the%20police%20station%20or%20the%20customer%20directly.%20Arijit%20Chatterjee%2C%20who%20left%20his%20belongings%20in%20an%20auto%2C%20managed%20to%20retrieve%20them%20the%20following%20morning%2C%20even%20though%20he%20did%20not%20have%20the%20driver%E2%80%99s%20or%20the%20auto%E2%80%99s%20license%20plate%20number%20as%20he%20hailed%20the%20auto%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20seen%20the%20%E2%80%98Smart%20City%20Auto%20Association%E2%80%99%20mentioned%20on%20the%20auto%20when%20I%20got%20off.%20So%20when%20I%20realised%20I%20had%20left%20my%20cards%20in%20the%20auto%2C%20I%20came%20across%20another%20auto%20with%20the%20same%20logo%20and%20told%20its%20driver%20what%20happened.%20He%20immediately%20informed%20the%20leader%20of%20their%20group%20who%20broadcasted%20the%20message%20in%20their%20circle.%20The%20auto%20driver%20who%20had%20ferried%20me%20called%20me%20within%20a%20few%20hours%20and%20handed%20over%20the%20valuables%20at%20my%20office%20the%20next%20morning%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arijit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAuto%20drivers%20turned%20social%20workers%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C