t%20demanded%20exorbitant%20fees%20from%20drivers%20for%20parking%20at%20stands%2C%20and%20consequently%2C%20he%20gained%20respect%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F288854%2Ftamil-nadu-auto-driver-daughter-tops-board-exams-after-fathers-heart-attack%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrivers%20within%20the%20city%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20association%E2%80%99s%20system%20is%20different.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20extort%20money%20to%20park%20in%20stands.%20We%20ensure%20that%20there%20is%20no%20fighting%20and%20that%20no%20one%20lifts%20a%20finger%20among%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20more%20and%20more%20drivers%20came%20around%20when%20they%20saw%20that%20he%20was%20indeed%20changing%20the%20status%20quo.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVenkat%20Senapathy%2C%20one%20of%20the%20founding%20members%20of%20the%20association%2C%20says%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20their%20problems%20were%20solved%20thanks%20to%20Dinabandhu%E2%80%99s%20initiative.%20%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20major%20problems%20was%20parking%20at%20the%20auto%20stand.%20We%20faced%20many%20difficulties%20with%20the%20Police%20too.%20Dinabandhu%E2%80%99s%20initiative%20took%20care%20of%20these%20issues.%20And%20now%20we%20have%20access%20to%20many%20facilities%20and%20feel%20good%20to%20be%20part%20of%20this%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesides%20social%20initiatives%2C%20Dinabandhu%20focused%20on%20bringing%20about%20behavioural%20change%20among%20auto%20drivers.%20To%20achieve%20this%2C%20the%20drivers%20were%20counselled%20and%20educated%20against%20bad%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20spoke%20to%20the%20drivers%20and%20told%20them%20not%20to%20drink%20and%20drive.%20If%20we%20find%20anyone%20driving%20drunk%2C%20we%20remove%20them%20from%20our%20association.%20The%20act%20of%20returning%20lost%20items%20to%20customers%20has%20also%20improved%20our%20image%20among%20the%20Police%2C%20who%20earlier%2C%20used%20to%20be%20frustrated%20with%20the%20drivers.%20Now%2C%20they%20listen%20to%20us%20and%20even%20call%20us%20for%20any%20emergency%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dinabandhu%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20glad%20that%20the%20public%20opinion%20has%20changed%20from%20negative%20to%20positive.%20The%20drivers%20provide%20their%20numbers%20at%20hospitals%20and%20blood%20banks%2C%20and%20also%20collect%20surplus%20food%20from%20weddings%20and%20other%20big%20events%20to%20distribute%20among%20the%20needy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20when%20the%20pandemic%20struck%20the%20state%2C%20the%20auto%20drivers%20stepped%20up%20to%20serve%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20ferried%20people%20for%20free%2C%20took%20patients%20to%20hospitals%2C%20and%20also%20carried%20oxygen%20cylinders.%20We%20pooled%20in%20for%20the%20medical%20treatment%20of%20drivers%20who%20fell%20sick.%20Unfortunately%2C%20we%20weren%E2%80%99t%20considered%20COVID%20warriors%20and%20the%20Government%20didn%E2%80%99t%20help%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Dinabandhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20informs%20that%20the%20driver%20group%20assisted%20their%20peers%2C%20covering%20medical%20expenses%20and%20immediate%20necessities%20for%20the%20families%20of%20drivers%20who%20lost%20their%20lives%20because%20of%20COVID.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20driver%20Deepak%20Sethi%20says%20that%20they%20feel%20satisfied%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20because%20they%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20help%20others.%20He%20adds%20that%20people%20see%20them%20in%20a%20different%20light%20today%2C%20and%20that%20makes%20him%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20we%20are%20not%20seen%20as%20only%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247298%2Flaibi-oinam-first-woman-auto-driver-manipur-documentary-meena-longjam-national-award-non-feature-covid-19-inspiring-san196%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edrivers%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20as%20social%20w