e%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20shows%20that%20adolescents%20in%20its%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magicbus.org%2Fuploads%2Fpdf%2FMB_Impact%2520Report%252022-23.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20programmes%20improved%20their%20school%20regularity%20by%2021.8%25%2C%20a%2031%25%20increase%20in%20perceived%20self-efficacy%2C%20and%20a%2034.7%25%20boost%20in%20resilience.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Baddi%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20place%20where%20Magic%20Bus%20has%20actively%20engaged%20since%202015%2C%20a%20significant%20milestone%20was%20reached%20in%20March%202021.%20The%20organisation%20introduced%20a%20sports%20programme%20exclusively%20tailored%20for%20girls.%20Divided%20into%20two%20distinct%20phases%20from%20December%202021%20to%20March%202023%2C%20this%20programme%20carries%20a%20primary%20objective%20of%20empowering%20girls%20aged%2011%20to%2018%20through%20the%20influence%20of%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Vivek%20Sharma%2C%20the%20programme%20manager%2C%2010%2C000%20girls%20were%20given%20sports%20sessions%20each%20in%20kabaddi%20or%20cricket.%20The%20girls%20also%20took%20part%20in%20tournaments%20within%20their%20schools.%20Some%20of%20them%20were%20then%20chosen%20to%20compete%20in%20district%2C%20state%2C%20and%20national%20tournaments.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20objectives%20of%20the%20programme%20also%20include%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20the%20participants%2C%20which%20includes%20communication%2C%20socio-emotional%20learning%2C%20and%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20says%20they%20were%20able%20to%20succeed%20in%20Baddi%20because%20Magic%20Bus%20had%20earned%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20trust%20first.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20been%20planning%20since%202015.%20We%20worked%20with%20the%20girls%2C%20the%20boys%20and%20their%20parents%20and%20sensitised%20them%20%5Bto%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20girls%E2%80%99%20sports%20programme%5D.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20programme%20has%20also%20actively%20addressed%20common%20concerns%20raised%20by%20parents%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F162218%2Fuber-cab-women-safety%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregarding%20the%20safety%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20expenses%20of%20the%20girls%20participating%20in%20tournaments%20held%20in%20larger%20cities.%20Recognising%20these%20concerns%2C%20the%20programme%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20the%20girls%E2%80%99%20expenses%20and%20ensures%20their%20safety%20by%20arranging%20for%20accompanying%20coaches%20during%20their%20travel.%20In%20certain%20cases%2C%20the%20programme%20even%20covers%20medical%20expenses%20and%20provides%20first%20aid%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVivek%20emphasises%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20way%2C%20we%20address%20any%20doubts%20community%20members%20may%20have%20about%20the%20program%2C%20ensuring%20that%20their%20questions%20are%20answered%20satisfactorily.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMatthew%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20when%20I%20played%20rugby%20with%20young%20people%2C%20I%20believed%20that%20helping%20them%20secure%20jobs%20would%20lead%20to%20economic%20stability.%20However%2C%20we%20realised%20they%20weren%E2%80%99t%20ready%20for%20a%20structured%20work%20environment.%20This%20setback%20inspired%20our%20%E2%80%9CChildhood%20to%20Livelihood%E2%80%9D%20programme.%20We%20understood%20that%20getting%20them%20jobs%20was%20only%20half%20the%20battle%3B%20keeping%20them%20employed%20required%20equipping%20them%20with%20the%20right%20skills%20and%20guidance%20to%20enter%20the%20workforce.%20It%E2%80%99s%20where%20they%20grasp%20the%20value%20of%20work%2C%20learn%20skills%20beyond%20their%20chosen%20profession%2C%20and%20evolve%20into%20role%20models%2C%20actively%20breaking%20the%20cycle%20of%20poverty%20for%20their%20families%20and%20the%20entire%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%2